# game/episode020.rpy:70
translate spanish episode020_b7e3e83f:

#   centered "{=chapter_heading}EPISODE 20{/=chapter_heading}"
    centered "{=chapter_heading}EPISODIO 20{/=chapter_heading}"

# game/episode020.rpy:73
translate spanish episode020_fbc9ddd2:

#   "Over the past few days, Eva consulted with Céline and Nadya for hours on end."
    "En los últimos días, Eva ha consultado durante horas a Céline y Nadya."

# game/episode020.rpy:75
translate spanish episode020_8d26ad6e:

#   "The medical staff wasn’t particularly happy with my sister exerting herself so soon after waking up, but they relented when they saw her thrive and getting healthier."
    "El personal médico no estaba muy contento con que mi hermana se esforzara tan pronto después de despertarse, pero cedieron cuando la vieron desarrollarse y estar cada vez más sana."

# game/episode020.rpy:76
translate spanish episode020_0dc94672:

#   "I’d talked to Eva a couple of times since she woke up, and while the initial mania had worn off, my sister was still determined to get to the bottom of her vision."
    "Había hablado con Eva un par de veces desde que se despertó y, aunque la manía inicial se le había pasado, mi hermana seguía decidida a llegar al fondo de su visión."

# game/episode020.rpy:78
translate spanish episode020_b0c18d29:

#   "The medical staff wasn’t particularly happy with Eva exerting herself so soon after waking up, but they relented when they saw her thrive and getting healthier."
    "El personal médico no estaba muy contento con que Eva se esforzara tan pronto después de despertarse, pero cedieron cuando la vieron desarrollarse y estar cada vez más sana."

# game/episode020.rpy:79
translate spanish episode020_a3070ef0:

#   "I’d talked to Eva a couple of times since she woke up, and while the initial mania had worn off, she was still determined to get to the bottom of her vision."
    "Había hablado con Eva un par de veces desde que se despertó y, aunque la manía inicial se le había pasado, seguía decidida a llegar al fondo de su visión."

# game/episode020.rpy:80
translate spanish episode020_233793d2:

#   "Once the doctors were satisfied Eva wasn’t going to lapse into a coma again, she was released from the medical wing and given her own room."
    "Cuando los médicos se cercioraron de que Eva no volvería a entrar en coma, la sacaron del ala médica y le dieron su propia habitación."

# game/episode020.rpy:81
translate spanish episode020_7c0e4ba2:

#   "She’d asked me to come by her room, where she would explain her findings together with Céline and Nadya."
    "Me había pedido que pasara por su habitación, donde explicaría sus hallazgos junto con Céline y Nadya."

# game/episode020.rpy:83
translate spanish episode020_f093dd67:

#   "They were already waiting for me as I entered."
    "Ya me estaban esperando cuando entré."

# game/episode020.rpy:84
translate spanish episode020_b55f93db:

#   c "I hope I didn’t keep you waiting."
    c "Espero no haberte hecho esperar."

# game/episode020.rpy:86
translate spanish episode020_9e12d5e8:

#   e "Not at all."
    e "En absoluto."

# game/episode020.rpy:88
translate spanish episode020_4272adbd:

#   e "Mom was early because she still can’t believe I’m doing well."
    e "Mamá llegó pronto porque aún no puede creer que me vaya bien."

# game/episode020.rpy:90
translate spanish episode020_dfa3d289:

#   e "Nadya was early because she still can’t believe I’m doing well."
    e "Nadya llegó pronto porque aún no puede creer que me vaya bien."

# game/episode020.rpy:92
translate spanish episode020_480e8640:

#   na "I just don’t want you to exert yourself."
    na "No quiero que te esfuerces."

# game/episode020.rpy:93
translate spanish episode020_b974d0c8:

#   na "The prophecy has been a mystery for quite some time, so there’s no need to stay up late and pour over astronavigation charts."
    na "La profecía ha sido un misterio durante bastante tiempo, así que no hay necesidad de trasnochar y revisar las cartas de astronavegación."

# game/episode020.rpy:94
translate spanish episode020_b4826250:

#   e "Agust and the Sovereignty were quite far along figuring out everything, just before we stole the Key from under their noses."
    e "Agustín y el Soberano estaban bastante avanzados en su comprensión de todo, justo antes de que les robáramos la Llave delante de sus narices."

# game/episode020.rpy:95
translate spanish episode020_89fcc289:

#   e "So I disagree on the no rush."
    e "Así que no estoy de acuerdo en que no haya prisa."

# game/episode020.rpy:96
translate spanish episode020_9139db3a:

#   na "Fair point."
    na "Buen punto."

# game/episode020.rpy:97
translate spanish episode020_55a9393e:

#   na "But we did steal the Key, so that’s quite a setback."
    na "Pero robamos la Llave, así que es todo un contratiempo."

# game/episode020.rpy:98
translate spanish episode020_d2b7e233:

#   e "True, but there’s no need to get complacent."
    e "Cierto, pero no hay que confiarse."

# game/episode020.rpy:99
translate spanish episode020_88df38a7:

#   c "Agreed."
    c "De acuerdo."

# game/episode020.rpy:100
translate spanish episode020_6a925ba1:

#   c "So what have you all learned?"
    c "¿Qué habéis aprendido?"

# game/episode020.rpy:101
translate spanish episode020_233cae3a:

#   e "I think we’ve found the system we need to travel to."
    e "Creo que hemos encontrado el sistema al que tenemos que viajar."

# game/episode020.rpy:103
translate spanish episode020_0f8fcd38:

#   ce "Based on Eva’s information, we were able to narrow the list of locations down to a manageable size."
    ce "Basándonos en la información de Eva, pudimos reducir la lista de lugares a un tamaño manejable."

# game/episode020.rpy:104
translate spanish episode020_b98772be:

#   c "There are multiple destinations?"
    c "¿Hay varios destinos?"

# game/episode020.rpy:105
translate spanish episode020_b7bef792:

#   ce "Only likely destinations, with the candidates sharing the most similarities with Eva’s vision and the prophecy at the top."
    ce "Sólo los destinos probables, con los candidatos que comparten más similitudes con la visión de Eva y la profecía en la parte superior."

# game/episode020.rpy:107
translate spanish episode020_3a0c9850:

#   e "I’m convinced the system at the top is the one we’re looking for."
    e "Estoy convencido de que el sistema de arriba es el que buscamos."

# game/episode020.rpy:108
translate spanish episode020_9b2e6f13:

#   e "The other candidates either lack some of the characteristics, or are in already heavily populated areas."
    e "Los demás candidatos carecen de algunas de estas características o se encuentran en zonas ya muy pobladas."

# game/episode020.rpy:109
translate spanish episode020_a03b4152:

#   c "So you’ve ruled out all of the inhabited planets?"
    c "¿Así que has descartado todos los planetas habitados?"

# game/episode020.rpy:111
translate spanish episode020_71de474d:

#   e "We did, the planet I saw in my vision was devoid of life."
    e "Lo hicimos, el planeta que vi en mi visión estaba desprovisto de vida."

# game/episode020.rpy:113
translate spanish episode020_d6d1b99b:

#   ce "The most promising system is called Petrarch, it’s situated in Držić, an ancient high-redshift galaxy in Ursa Major."
    ce "El sistema más prometedor se llama Petrarca, está situado en Držić, una antigua galaxia de alto desplazamiento al rojo en la Osa Mayor."

# game/episode020.rpy:114
translate spanish episode020_58eff1e7:

#   c "Ancient?"
    c "¿Antiguo?"

# game/episode020.rpy:116
translate spanish episode020_74d294b1:

#   na "Yes, billions of years old, formed when the universe was still very young."
    na "Sí, miles de millones de años, formado cuando el universo era aún muy joven."

# game/episode020.rpy:118
translate spanish episode020_c1228a22:

#   e "It fits all the criteria."
    e "Cumple todos los criterios."

# game/episode020.rpy:119
translate spanish episode020_f70f4742:

#   e "Petrarch contains several planets, mostly gas giants and one terrestrial."
    e "Petrarca contiene varios planetas, en su mayoría gigantes gaseosos y uno terrestre."

# game/episode020.rpy:120
translate spanish episode020_fd046101:

#   e "Those planets all orbit three stars."
    e "Todos esos planetas orbitan alrededor de tres estrellas."

# game/episode020.rpy:121
translate spanish episode020_c85ce1b8:

#   c "With you so far."
    c "Contigo hasta ahora."

# game/episode020.rpy:122
translate spanish episode020_0cae4ed9:

#   c "And Petrarch experienced the after effects of a star going nova?"
    c "¿Y Petrarca experimentó las secuelas de una estrella que se convierte en nova?"

# game/episode020.rpy:123
translate spanish episode020_dc5b4b47:

#   e "No, we considered that."
    e "No, lo hemos considerado."

# game/episode020.rpy:124
translate spanish episode020_eb012489:

#   e "But ‘the dying light’ could also stand for something else."
    e "Pero \"la luz moribunda\" también podría significar otra cosa."

# game/episode020.rpy:126
translate spanish episode020_433e3d08:

#   ce "A dying star, for example."
    ce "Una estrella moribunda, por ejemplo."

# game/episode020.rpy:128
translate spanish episode020_8e433c85:

#   e "The curious thing about the three stars of Petrarch is that they’re all dying."
    e "Lo curioso de las tres estrellas de Petrarca es que se están muriendo."

# game/episode020.rpy:129
translate spanish episode020_8c76b7c8:

#   c "The stars are collapsing at the same time?"
    c "¿Las estrellas están colapsando al mismo tiempo?"

# game/episode020.rpy:131
translate spanish episode020_6e8fd083:

#   ce "Yes, they appear to be."
    ce "Sí, eso parece."

# game/episode020.rpy:132
translate spanish episode020_d3449d60:

#   c "That’s rare, isn’t it?"
    c "Eso es raro, ¿no?"

# game/episode020.rpy:134
translate spanish episode020_3e9f9002:

#   ce "Rare, but not unheard of."
    ce "Raro, pero no inaudito."

# game/episode020.rpy:136
translate spanish episode020_8731a38a:

#   e "It all fits, [p_name_short]."
    e "Todo encaja, [p_name_short]."

# game/episode020.rpy:137
translate spanish episode020_8b00435a:

#   e "I think this is the place we need to go to."
    e "Creo que este es el lugar al que tenemos que ir."

# game/episode020.rpy:138
translate spanish episode020_ee2bf491:

#   c "It’s worth a shot."
    c "Vale la pena intentarlo."

# game/episode020.rpy:139
translate spanish episode020_19337a7f:

#   c "Let’s do it then, as soon as you’re fit enough to leave."
    c "Hagámoslo entonces, en cuanto estés en condiciones de salir."

# game/episode020.rpy:141
translate spanish episode020_d7a7e324:

#   na "There’s a but."
    na "Hay un pero."

# game/episode020.rpy:142
translate spanish episode020_c7a1defc:

#   c "There always is."
    c "Siempre lo hay."

# game/episode020.rpy:144
translate spanish episode020_3b37783a:

#   na "According to Thyia, the systems neighboring Petrarch are a notorious mess."
    na "Según Thyia, los sistemas vecinos a Petrarca son un notorio caos."

# game/episode020.rpy:145
translate spanish episode020_363a544c:

#   na "Several of Petrarch’s neighbors are at war with each other and because of the chaos there’s rampant piracy."
    na "Varios vecinos de Petrarca están en guerra entre sí y, debido al caos, hay una piratería desenfrenada."

# game/episode020.rpy:147
translate spanish episode020_885b6596:

#   na "The few remaining trade ships that were willing to deal with the warlords and the pirates halted operations years ago."
    na "Los pocos barcos comerciales que estaban dispuestos a tratar con los señores de la guerra y los piratas interrumpieron sus operaciones hace años."

# game/episode020.rpy:148
translate spanish episode020_dab698e2:

#   c "How come?"
    c "¿Por qué?"

# game/episode020.rpy:150
translate spanish episode020_6ec0b88f:

#   ce "Probably because several ships were sent back to their owners flying on autopilot and every single member of the crew dismembered."
    ce "Probablemente porque varias naves fueron devueltas a sus propietarios volando con el piloto automático y todos y cada uno de los miembros de la tripulación desmembrados."

# game/episode020.rpy:151
translate spanish episode020_128a100d:

#   ce "Most shipping companies might care little for the personal welfare of their employees, but before long they had trouble even finding crew members willing to make the journey."
    ce "Puede que a la mayoría de las compañías navieras les importara poco el bienestar personal de sus empleados, pero al poco tiempo tuvieron problemas incluso para encontrar tripulantes dispuestos a hacer el viaje."

# game/episode020.rpy:152
translate spanish episode020_87563436:

#   c "I guess they started to care after that."
    c "Supongo que empezaron a preocuparse después de eso."

# game/episode020.rpy:154
translate spanish episode020_c43a6cba:

#   ce "They sure did."
    ce "Claro que sí."

# game/episode020.rpy:155
translate spanish episode020_29cfb54b:

#   c "You’ve spoken to Thyia about all this, Nadya?"
    c "¿Has hablado con Thyia de todo esto, Nadya?"

# game/episode020.rpy:157
translate spanish episode020_57e6ff21:

#   na "I did, yes."
    na "Lo hice, sí."

# game/episode020.rpy:158
translate spanish episode020_170f2a33:

#   c "So she’s familiar with the situation there?"
    c "¿Así que está familiarizada con la situación allí?"

# game/episode020.rpy:160
translate spanish episode020_2c274c5b:

#   na "Not exactly, but she knows of the situation."
    na "No exactamente, pero conoce la situación."

# game/episode020.rpy:161
translate spanish episode020_6b6d0156:

#   na "You should speak to her and see if she has any more details."
    na "Deberías hablar con ella y ver si tiene más detalles."

# game/episode020.rpy:162
translate spanish episode020_255ecca1:

#   c "I will."
    c "Lo haré."

# game/episode020.rpy:164
translate spanish episode020_87c7c811:

#   e "But we’re going, right?"
    e "Pero nos vamos, ¿verdad?"

# game/episode020.rpy:165
translate spanish episode020_132c0d7c:

#   c "Yes, we are, even if we have to hire a personal army to get us through that place."
    c "Sí, lo haremos, aunque tengamos que contratar un ejército personal para atravesar ese lugar."

# game/episode020.rpy:166
translate spanish episode020_810bfab1:

#   c "But we need some more intel first."
    c "Pero primero necesitamos más información."

# game/episode020.rpy:167
translate spanish episode020_068119dd:

#   c "I’ll speak to Thyia and maybe Jade can rummage the net to see if there’s anything on Petrarch and the adjoining systems?"
    c "Hablaré con Thyia y quizá Jade pueda rebuscar en la red para ver si hay algo sobre Petrarch y los sistemas colindantes."

# game/episode020.rpy:169
translate spanish episode020_0a6c3489:

#   ce "Good idea, I’ll ask her."
    ce "Buena idea, le preguntaré."

# game/episode020.rpy:262
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_cd291b8b:

#   "Over the course of several days, our strategy for getting into Petrarch territory had become much clearer."
    "A lo largo de varios días, nuestra estrategia para adentrarnos en territorio petrarquista se había vuelto mucho más clara."

# game/episode020.rpy:263
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_e071480d:

#   "Everyone was in agreement that we should take up the bounty Jade had found and try to bargain our way through the contested space surrounding Petrarch."
    "Todos estaban de acuerdo en que debíamos aceptar la recompensa que había encontrado Jade e intentar regatear para abrirnos paso por el disputado espacio que rodea Petrarch."

# game/episode020.rpy:264
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_12109f2f:

#   "Thyia was in charge of reaching out to the pirate band that had posted the bounty."
    "Thyia se encargó de contactar con la banda pirata que había puesto la recompensa."

# game/episode020.rpy:265
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_5b70afef:

#   "Late during the day, Thyia messaged to tell me she’d made some progress."
    "A última hora del día, Thyia me envió un mensaje para decirme que había hecho algunos progresos."

# game/episode020.rpy:267
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_b8393557:

#   "I went to see her together with Eva on the landing pad where the Bastard was parked."
    "Fui a verla junto con Eva a la pista de aterrizaje donde estaba aparcado el Bastardo."

# game/episode020.rpy:268
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_4c39030f:

#   c "Have they agreed to meet us?"
    c "¿Han accedido a reunirse con nosotros?"

# game/episode020.rpy:270
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_ff50648b:

#   th "They have."
    th "Tienen."

# game/episode020.rpy:271
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_64b4acda:

#   th "We are to meet the pirate queen Xile and her fleet at the coordinates they’ve sent us."
    th "Debemos encontrarnos con la reina pirata Xile y su flota en las coordenadas que nos han enviado."

# game/episode020.rpy:273
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_7424152d:

#   e "Are we to discuss terms with them?"
    e "¿Vamos a discutir las condiciones con ellos?"

# game/episode020.rpy:275
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_fd3c3bb3:

#   th "I reckon so."
    th "Creo que sí."

# game/episode020.rpy:276
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_d26c58dd:

#   c "Do you know anything about this Xile?"
    c "¿Sabes algo de este Xile?"

# game/episode020.rpy:277
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_fe4086d1:

#   th "Not much."
    th "No mucho."

# game/episode020.rpy:278
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_f1f5a9ed:

#   th "She’s been queen for quite a long time and seems fair and evenhanded, as far as pirates go."
    th "Ha sido reina durante bastante tiempo y parece justa y ecuánime, en lo que respecta a los piratas."

# game/episode020.rpy:279
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_5fdec604:

#   c "So, less of a psycho compared to most of them."
    c "Así que, menos psicópata comparado con la mayoría de ellos."

# game/episode020.rpy:280
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_6e8fc06a:

#   c "That’s got to count for something."
    c "Eso tiene que contar para algo."

# game/episode020.rpy:282
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_88f19a75:

#   th "Quite right."
    th "Muy cierto."

# game/episode020.rpy:284
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_2b608244:

#   e "We’ll be leaving shortly then?"
    e "¿Nos iremos pronto entonces?"

# game/episode020.rpy:285
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_cc5c7e87:

#   c "Yes, let’s round up the others and tell them we’ll leave paradise."
    c "Sí, reunamos a los demás y digámosles que nos iremos del paraíso."

# game/episode020.rpy:304
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_9b6bf3aa:

#   "I returned to my bedroom to tell Raene we were leaving."
    "Volví a mi habitación para decirle a Raene que nos íbamos."

# game/episode020.rpy:305
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_b0154d87:

#   "Entering the room I immediately felt something was amiss."
    "Al entrar en la habitación, inmediatamente sentí que algo iba mal."

# game/episode020.rpy:306
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_d9ea7f40:

#   c "Raene?"
    c "¿Raene?"

# game/episode020.rpy:308
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_5e3eb0be:

#   "The balcony and bathroom were empty."
    "El balcón y el baño estaban vacíos."

# game/episode020.rpy:309
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_194f8173:

#   "There were no signs of struggle, but Raene’s absence triggered an instant panic."
    "No había signos de lucha, pero la ausencia de Raene desencadenó un pánico instantáneo."

# game/episode020.rpy:311
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_b36994dc:

#   "I messaged every crew member to ask them if they had been in contact with Raene."
    "Envié mensajes a todos los miembros de la tripulación para preguntarles si habían estado en contacto con Raene."

# game/episode020.rpy:312
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_f258c9fe:

#   "Nobody had heard anything from her in the past few hours."
    "Nadie había sabido nada de ella en las últimas horas."

# game/episode020.rpy:313
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_982a67fc:

#   "I asked Jade to come to my room."
    "Le pedí a Jade que viniera a mi habitación."

# game/episode020.rpy:315
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_ece09f3d:

#   "While she was on her way, I donned my armor and checked my weapon."
    "Mientras ella seguía su camino, me puse la armadura y comprobé mi arma."

# game/episode020.rpy:317
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_82ab2dcc:

#   j "Did something bad happen to Raene?"
    j "¿Le pasó algo malo a Raene?"

# game/episode020.rpy:318
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_aa6ff30f:

#   c "I’m not sure, but she wouldn’t leave this room willingly."
    c "No estoy seguro, pero no saldría de esta habitación de buena gana."

# game/episode020.rpy:319
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_19c0334d:

#   c "There are clerics from her father’s church here and they might know she’s here."
    c "Hay clérigos de la iglesia de su padre aquí y puede que sepan que está aquí."

# game/episode020.rpy:321
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_fc96c41b:

#   j "Would she open the door for them?"
    j "¿Les abriría la puerta?"

# game/episode020.rpy:322
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_16932397:

#   c "Absolutely not."
    c "Por supuesto que no."

# game/episode020.rpy:323
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_a0979f88:

#   c "But they might have tricked her."
    c "Pero podrían haberla engañado."

# game/episode020.rpy:324
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_efbd6a7e:

#   c "Can you find out where those clerics are staying in the Residence?"
    c "¿Puedes averiguar dónde se alojan esos clérigos en la Residencia?"

# game/episode020.rpy:326
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_2ea23ada:

#   j "Of course, I’ll get right on it."
    j "Por supuesto, me pondré a ello."

# game/episode020.rpy:328
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_e2d5ce36:

#   "Jade hooked her tablet into the Residence network and started typing furiously."
    "Jade conectó su tableta a la red de la Residencia y empezó a teclear furiosamente."

# game/episode020.rpy:329
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_4ad5e2c8:

#   "I paced the room, trying not to let my worries get the upper hand."
    "Me paseé por la habitación, intentando que mis preocupaciones no me dominaran."

# game/episode020.rpy:330
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_907db104:

#   "After an agonizing half hour Jade looked up at me in triumph."
    "Después de una agonizante media hora, Jade me miró triunfante."

# game/episode020.rpy:332
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_b0925680:

#   j "Got it!"
    j "¡La tengo!"

# game/episode020.rpy:333
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_26801211:

#   j "They’re staying on the fifth floor of the Residence, room 5038."
    j "Se alojan en la quinta planta de la Residencia, habitación 5038."

# game/episode020.rpy:335
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_8df3d61a:

#   j "I’ve also found an incident report from that same floor."
    j "También he encontrado un informe de incidentes de ese mismo piso."

# game/episode020.rpy:336
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_e7bbbaaa:

#   j "The management of the Residence was alerted by one of the guests about a disturbance earlier today."
    j "La dirección de la Residencia fue alertada por uno de los huéspedes sobre un disturbio ocurrido hoy temprano."

# game/episode020.rpy:337
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_221ff76d:

#   j "Someone complaining about shouting in the hallway."
    j "Alguien quejándose de gritos en el pasillo."

# game/episode020.rpy:338
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_838256c8:

#   j "When they went to check it out the shouting had stopped."
    j "Cuando fueron a comprobarlo, los gritos habían cesado."

# game/episode020.rpy:339
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_1ec4b2e4:

#   c "Those fuckers!"
    c "¡Esos cabrones!"

# game/episode020.rpy:340
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_0b8b92a5:

#   c "I’m going to have a conversation with them..."
    c "Voy a tener una conversación con ellos..."

# game/episode020.rpy:341
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_147fa014:

#   c "Alert the others and tell them we might need to leave in a hurry."
    c "Alerta a los demás y diles que puede que tengamos que irnos deprisa."

# game/episode020.rpy:343
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_6214d03c:

#   j "Do you need backup?"
    j "¿Necesitas refuerzos?"

# game/episode020.rpy:344
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_e66c9b2c:

#   c "Yes, send Aven and Kit to the fifth floor, armed and suited up."
    c "Sí, envía a Aven y a Kit al quinto piso, armados y vestidos."

# game/episode020.rpy:345
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_936de881:

#   c "Could you open the door for me remotely as soon as I’m on the fifth floor?"
    c "¿Podría abrirme la puerta a distancia en cuanto esté en la quinta planta?"

# game/episode020.rpy:347
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_e8462428:

#   j "Got it."
    j "Entendido."

# game/episode020.rpy:349
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_a59c5cb2:

#   j "Good luck, [p_name]."
    j "Buena suerte, [p_name]."

# game/episode020.rpy:351
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_8a5c331b:

#   j "Good luck, [p_name_short]."
    j "Buena suerte, [p_name_short]."

# game/episode020.rpy:352
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_7d7a13b3:

#   "Leaving Jade behind, I sped through the corridors of the Residence to one of the elevators."
    "Dejando atrás a Jade, me dirigí a toda velocidad por los pasillos de la Residencia hacia uno de los ascensores."

# game/episode020.rpy:354
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_f106f196:

#   "The elevator took me up to the fifth floor, revealing a similar hallway."
    "El ascensor me llevó a la quinta planta, donde había un pasillo similar."

# game/episode020.rpy:355
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_b8800ba2:

#   "Room 5038 was near the end of the corridor."
    "La habitación 5038 estaba cerca del final del pasillo."

# game/episode020.rpy:357
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_93c03ce3:

#   "I messaged Jade that I was in position and ready for her to open the door."
    "Le envié un mensaje a Jade diciéndole que estaba en posición y listo para que abriera la puerta."

# game/episode020.rpy:358
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_9a551b96:

#   "After a minute the door slid open, I pulled my gun and prepared to step inside."
    "Al cabo de un minuto, la puerta se abrió, saqué mi pistola y me preparé para entrar."

# game/episode020.rpy:360
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_e1db797e:

#   man "Who’s there?"
    man "¿Quién está ahí?"

# game/episode020.rpy:362
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_0e37e0b2:

#   "One of the clerics came to check on the door and suddenly stared into the barrel of my gun."
    "Uno de los clérigos vino a comprobar la puerta y, de repente, clavó los ojos en el cañón de mi pistola."

# game/episode020.rpy:363
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_6eff4eb3:

#   c "Hands up where I can see them."
    c "Manos arriba donde pueda verlas."

# game/episode020.rpy:364
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_48c678cf:

#   c "Slowly turn around and take me to the others."
    c "Gírate despacio y llévame con los demás."

# game/episode020.rpy:366
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_229a2e07:

#   "The cleric complied and led me to the living area."
    "El clérigo obedeció y me condujo a la sala de estar."

# game/episode020.rpy:367
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_82a5c493:

#   "I couldn’t suppress a sigh of relief when I saw Raene sitting on the couch unharmed."
    "No pude reprimir un suspiro de alivio cuando vi a Raene sentada en el sofá, ilesa."

# game/episode020.rpy:368
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_4f792e40:

#   "She was surrounded by the other two clerics and looking at the video screen on the opposite wall."
    "Estaba rodeada por los otros dos clérigos y miraba la pantalla de vídeo de la pared opuesta."

# game/episode020.rpy:370
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_8b24ee79:

#   "A familiar face was apparently having a one-sided chat with Raene."
    "Al parecer, una cara conocida mantenía una charla unilateral con Raene."

# game/episode020.rpy:371
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_64bfc918:

#   sa "You are to return with Father Morray."
    sa "Debes regresar con el Padre Morray."

# game/episode020.rpy:372
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_74cc63f0:

#   sa "As soon as you’re home, we’ll be able to reverse the dreadful things you’ve done to yourself."
    sa "En cuanto estés en casa, podremos revertir las cosas terribles que te has hecho."

# game/episode020.rpy:373
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_c4e61ee4:

#   sa "And begin your re-education, of course."
    sa "Y comenzar su reeducación, por supuesto."

# game/episode020.rpy:374
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_51321de4:

#   sa "I can’t belief my very own son has strayed so far from the righteous path."
    sa "No puedo creer que mi propio hijo se haya desviado tanto del camino recto."

# game/episode020.rpy:376
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_0d365eea:

#   ra "I’m not your son and I haven’t strayed."
    ra "No soy tu hijo y no me he desviado."

# game/episode020.rpy:377
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_e46011f2:

#   ra "I’m finally the person who I want to be."
    ra "Por fin soy la persona que quiero ser."

# game/episode020.rpy:379
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_1d27e859:

#   sa "Don’t talk nonsense, Arion."
    sa "No digas tonterías, Arion."

# game/episode020.rpy:381
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_6cdc2a40:

#   ra "That’s not my name!"
    ra "¡Ese no es mi nombre!"

# game/episode020.rpy:383
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_6c14cee4:

#   sa "It is, boy, do not delude yourself."
    sa "Lo es, muchacho, no te engañes."

# game/episode020.rpy:384
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_15da3c30:

#   sa "Don’t tell me you’re still calling yourself that name you’ve invented for yourself."
    sa "No me digas que sigues llamándote con ese nombre que te has inventado."

# game/episode020.rpy:385
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_d69ec423:

#   sa "The one that so clearly defiles the given name of my dearly departed wife Raenata."
    sa "El que tan claramente mancilla el nombre de pila de mi querida difunta esposa Raenata."

# game/episode020.rpy:387
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_a01360ce:

#   ra "Mother supported me, she would have been proud of me!"
    ra "Mi madre me apoyó, ¡habría estado orgullosa de mí!"

# game/episode020.rpy:389
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_777f6567:

#   sa "That’s quite enough, Arion."
    sa "Es suficiente, Arion."

# game/episode020.rpy:390
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_dc409cc7:

#   sa "God granted us a son and the things you’ve done to yourself are an affront to His Good Works as well as the love we’ve given you over the years."
    sa "Dios nos concedió un hijo y las cosas que te has hecho son una afrenta a Sus Buenas Obras así como al amor que te hemos dado a lo largo de los años."

# game/episode020.rpy:392
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_bb780236:

#   ra "I don’t-"
    ra "Yo no..."

# game/episode020.rpy:394
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_dda8f63d:

#   sa "Silence, Arion!"
    sa "¡Silencio, Arion!"

# game/episode020.rpy:395
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_31c97456:

#   sa "You will obey your father!"
    sa "¡Obedecerás a tu padre!"

# game/episode020.rpy:397
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_6d5b6272:

#   c "If you speak that name again I’ll be forced to shoot one of your altar boys in the head, Sacleus."
    c "Si vuelves a pronunciar ese nombre me veré obligado a disparar a uno de tus monaguillos en la cabeza, Sacleus."

# game/episode020.rpy:398
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_d667636e:

#   "Everyone had their eyes glued to the video screen before, so they only noticed me standing in the room as I spoke."
    "Antes todos tenían los ojos pegados a la pantalla de vídeo, así que sólo se fijaron en mí, de pie en la sala, mientras hablaba."

# game/episode020.rpy:400
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_96d563f1:

#   ra "[p_name_short]!"
    ra "¡[p_name_short]!"

# game/episode020.rpy:401
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_7c294a9f:

#   sa "What’s the meaning of this?"
    sa "¿Qué significa esto?"

# game/episode020.rpy:402
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_ebea6ff7:

#   sa "Is this the heretic who led you astray?"
    sa "¿Es este el hereje que te llevó por mal camino?"

# game/episode020.rpy:403
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_98c7c822:

#   sa "Seize him!"
    sa "¡Atrápenlo!"

# game/episode020.rpy:404
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_9f2ae320:

#   c "I wouldn’t do that, if I were you."
    c "Yo no haría eso, si fuera tú."

# game/episode020.rpy:405
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_60353569:

#   "Both clerics were aware of the gun trained on the back of their colleague’s head and hesitated."
    "Ambos clérigos fueron conscientes de la pistola apuntando a la nuca de su colega y dudaron."

# game/episode020.rpy:406
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_a22550b0:

#   c "You’ve taken Raene against her will with the intent to ship her off this planet."
    c "Te has llevado a Raene contra su voluntad con la intención de enviarla fuera de este planeta."

# game/episode020.rpy:407
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_2a030f06:

#   c "I’m sure the Residence officials will be very interested to learn about what happened here."
    c "Estoy seguro de que los funcionarios de la Residencia estarán muy interesados en saber lo que ha ocurrido aquí."

# game/episode020.rpy:409
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_654e9348:

#   sa "It’s my blood you’re talking about, I have every right to-"
    sa "Estás hablando de mi sangre, tengo todo el derecho a..."

# game/episode020.rpy:410
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_47977152:

#   c "Judging from the way you were just talking to her, I’d say you have very little respect for Raene."
    c "A juzgar por la forma en que le hablabas, diría que tienes muy poco respeto por Raene."

# game/episode020.rpy:411
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_f021c479:

#   c "And I’m very sure she doesn’t want to be reunited with you."
    c "Y estoy muy seguro de que no quiere reunirse contigo."

# game/episode020.rpy:412
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_b1ff5e70:

#   c "Am I correct, Raene?"
    c "¿Estoy en lo cierto, Raene?"

# game/episode020.rpy:414
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_2dc56006:

#   ra "No, I don’t want to go back to my father."
    ra "No, no quiero volver con mi padre."

# game/episode020.rpy:416
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_ff4787dc:

#   sa "You’ve corrupted him!"
    sa "¡Lo has corrompido!"

# game/episode020.rpy:417
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_2015fd33:

#   sa "Tempted him with your wicked sinful ways!"
    sa "¡Lo tentaste con tus malvados caminos pecaminosos!"

# game/episode020.rpy:418
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_b3f912b1:

#   c "I’m sure you believe that."
    c "Seguro que te lo crees."

# game/episode020.rpy:419
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_ef1adb1a:

#   c "I call it loving someone."
    c "Yo lo llamo amar a alguien."

# game/episode020.rpy:420
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_0f0ad03b:

#   c "Here’s what’s going to happen though."
    c "Sin embargo, esto es lo que va a pasar."

# game/episode020.rpy:421
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_d9fc4d91:

#   c "I’m going to walk out with Raene unharmed and you will not pursue us."
    c "Saldré con Raene ileso y no nos perseguirás."

# game/episode020.rpy:422
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_241b344c:

#   c "If you do, I’ll make sure to kill you three and make a convincing case of it being self-defence."
    c "Si lo hacéis, me aseguraré de mataros a los tres y de argumentar de forma convincente que fue en defensa propia."

# game/episode020.rpy:424
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_16c45d30:

#   av "Are you okay in there?"
    av "¿Estás bien ahí dentro?"

# game/episode020.rpy:425
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_40e80566:

#   c "Backup has also just arrived."
    c "También acaba de llegar la copia de seguridad."

# game/episode020.rpy:426
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_ebe16fee:

#   c "I think it’s time to go, Raene."
    c "Creo que es hora de irnos, Raene."

# game/episode020.rpy:428
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_0b760eba:

#   "Raene got up and neither of the two clerics prevented her from walking toward me."
    "Raene se levantó y ninguno de los dos clérigos le impidió caminar hacia mí."

# game/episode020.rpy:429
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_0927ad9d:

#   sa "Get back here at once!"
    sa "¡Vuelve aquí de inmediato!"

# game/episode020.rpy:430
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_c29b2ad9:

#   sa "You belong with me!"
    sa "¡Tú perteneces a mí!"

# game/episode020.rpy:432
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_675feea1:

#   ra "No, I do not."
    ra "No, no lo creo."

# game/episode020.rpy:433
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_2dcd7e61:

#   ra "You’ve never respected the person I am and judging from the way you’ve treated me just now, you never will."
    ra "Nunca has respetado a la persona que soy y, a juzgar por cómo me has tratado ahora, nunca lo harás."

# game/episode020.rpy:434
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_9e2e746f:

#   ra "I don’t want to see you ever again, father."
    ra "No quiero volver a verte, padre."

# game/episode020.rpy:435
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_439802a1:

#   ra "Goodbye."
    ra "Adiós."

# game/episode020.rpy:437
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_5481f9d2:

#   "Protected by Aven, Kit and me, Raene walked out of the room, her head held high."
    "Protegida por Aven, Kit y yo, Raene salió de la habitación con la cabeza bien alta."

# game/episode020.rpy:438
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_bfb2520b:

#   "Sacleus could still be heard raging inside the room."
    "Todavía se oía a Sacleus enfurecido dentro de la habitación."

# game/episode020.rpy:440
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_594bc868:

#   c "That was very brave of you."
    c "Eso fue muy valiente de tu parte."

# game/episode020.rpy:441
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_a8ebf496:

#   ra "I was scared to death."
    ra "Estaba muerto de miedo."

# game/episode020.rpy:443
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_3e72eda9:

#   ra "Still, I felt it had to be said."
    ra "Aun así, sentí que debía decirlo."

# game/episode020.rpy:444
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_85021674:

#   c "It sure did."
    c "Claro que sí."

# game/episode020.rpy:446
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_6ca20477:

#   ra "It won’t change my father’s opinion though."
    ra "Pero eso no cambiará la opinión de mi padre."

# game/episode020.rpy:447
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_49d06e6c:

#   c "It probably won’t, but that wasn’t the point."
    c "Probablemente no lo haga, pero no se trataba de eso."

# game/episode020.rpy:449
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_67df49a2:

#   ra "No, I think you’re right."
    ra "No, creo que tienes razón."

# game/episode020.rpy:451
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_93bb2d8c:

#   av "The Bastard is waiting for us on the landing pad."
    av "El Bastardo nos espera en la pista de aterrizaje."

# game/episode020.rpy:452
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_45930ac3:

#   c "Do you need anything from your room, Raene?"
    c "¿Necesitas algo de tu habitación, Raene?"

# game/episode020.rpy:453
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_ae9dc50d:

#   ki "Céline and Lilly have already packed your things."
    ki "Céline y Lilly ya han empaquetado tus cosas."

# game/episode020.rpy:454
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_1f8dfc4a:

#   ra "In that case I’m good to go."
    ra "En ese caso, estoy listo."

# game/episode020.rpy:456
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_3389b9fa:

#   "We hurried to the landing pad, worried about the clerics raising the alarm."
    "Nos apresuramos a la pista de aterrizaje, preocupados por si los clérigos daban la alarma."

# game/episode020.rpy:457
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_57785808:

#   "Luckily, our display of force seemed to have paid off."
    "Por suerte, nuestro despliegue de fuerza pareció dar resultado."

# game/episode020.rpy:462
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_18f15baf:

#   "Unchallenged by any clerics, we took off from Paclerara and made our way to the point where we’d meet up with Xile."
    "Sin ser desafiados por ningún clérigo, salimos de Paclerara y nos dirigimos al punto donde nos encontraríamos con Xile."

# game/episode020.rpy:464
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_f36a18b0:

#   "The following hours were spent packing and preparing the Bastard for another journey."
    "Las horas siguientes las pasamos empaquetando y preparando el Bastardo para otro viaje."

# game/episode020.rpy:469
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_departure_69567ca7:

#   "We took off from Paclerara and made our way to the point where we’d meet up with Xile."
    "Salimos de Paclerara y nos dirigimos al punto donde nos encontraríamos con Xile."

# game/episode020.rpy:477
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_missing_63fc1a7a:

#   "We were about to depart when I got a message from Thyia."
    "Estábamos a punto de partir cuando recibí un mensaje de Thyia."

# game/episode020.rpy:479
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_missing_cc936102:

#   "I hurried to the landing pad where she was waiting for me."
    "Me apresuré a llegar a la pista de aterrizaje, donde ella me esperaba."

# game/episode020.rpy:480
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_missing_c74505e2:

#   c "What’s the matter?"
    c "¿Cuál es el problema?"

# game/episode020.rpy:482
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_missing_54ea6d9b:

#   th "We’re one person short."
    th "Nos falta una persona."

# game/episode020.rpy:483
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_missing_199aa782:

#   c "Who?"
    c "¿A quién?"

# game/episode020.rpy:485
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_missing_5a7e5203:

#   th "Thim didn’t check in."
    th "Thim no se registró."

# game/episode020.rpy:486
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_missing_88c02de1:

#   c "Didn’t he get the message?"
    c "¿No entendió el mensaje?"

# game/episode020.rpy:488
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_missing_52480505:

#   th "He did."
    th "Lo hizo."

# game/episode020.rpy:489
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_missing_83ac829a:

#   th "I sent out Vess to check."
    th "Envié a Vess a comprobarlo."

# game/episode020.rpy:490
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_missing_39f4deef:

#   th "According to her, his room in the Residence is empty."
    th "Según ella, su habitación en la Residencia está vacía."

# game/episode020.rpy:491
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_missing_73baf10e:

#   th "Jade just verified that he checked himself out two hours ago."
    th "Jade acaba de verificar que se dio de baja hace dos horas."

# game/episode020.rpy:492
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_missing_b437b351:

#   c "Fuck."
    c "Joder."

# game/episode020.rpy:493
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_missing_0977fdc7:

#   c "He made a run for it?"
    c "¿Hizo una carrera?"

# game/episode020.rpy:495
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_missing_2ffd728a:

#   th "It seems so."
    th "Eso parece."

# game/episode020.rpy:496
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_missing_493a46ca:

#   c "Is he still on Paclerara?"
    c "¿Sigue en Paclerara?"

# game/episode020.rpy:497
