# game/episode020.rpy:1045
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_kit_d2457df7:

#   c "The ship is full enough as it is."
    c "El barco ya está bastante lleno."

# game/episode020.rpy:1047
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_kit_27bdbc08:

#   ki "I know."
    ki "Lo sé."

# game/episode020.rpy:1048
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_kit_e2eac783:

#   ki "Just enjoying myself for the duration of our stay."
    ki "Simplemente disfrutando durante nuestra estancia."

# game/episode020.rpy:1049
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_kit_564a7470:

#   c "We’ve made some progress on the prophecy front."
    c "Hemos hecho algunos progresos en el frente de la profecía."

# game/episode020.rpy:1050
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_kit_a86e0f2a:

#   ki "Oh, good."
    ki "Oh, bien."

# game/episode020.rpy:1051
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_kit_3dfcf173:

#   c "Just read the messages that were sent to you in between sessions, or whatever."
    c "Sólo tienes que leer los mensajes que te han enviado entre sesión y sesión, o lo que sea."

# game/episode020.rpy:1052
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_kit_f3ba7290:

#   ki "I will."
    ki "Lo haré."

# game/episode020.rpy:1054
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_kit_d0c8b827:

#   c "Oh, and I want to call a meeting about Thim."
    c "Ah, y quiero convocar una reunión sobre Thim."

# game/episode020.rpy:1055
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_kit_e34d54d4:

#   ki "I’ll be there."
    ki "Allí estaré."

# game/episode020.rpy:1056
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_kit_2b9f897e:

#   c "Well, I’ll leave you to it then."
    c "Bueno, te dejo con ello entonces."

# game/episode020.rpy:1057
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_kit_1aa4f527:

#   c "Remember we don’t have medical insurance, in case your dick falls off because of over-exertion."
    c "Recuerda que no tenemos seguro médico, por si se te cae la polla por un sobreesfuerzo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1059
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_kit_97ed3740:

#   ki "Pllxytlxx is as a tender lover, especially when it comes to my private parts."
    ki "Pllxytlxx es como un tierno amante, especialmente cuando se trata de mis partes íntimas."

# game/episode020.rpy:1060
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_kit_5e467c9e:

#   c "Far too much detail!"
    c "Demasiados detalles."

# game/episode020.rpy:1061
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_kit_760e1211:

#   c "Going now."
    c "Vamos ahora."

# game/episode020.rpy:1063
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_kit_1ecc6b97:

#   ki "See you soon."
    ki "Hasta pronto."

# game/episode020.rpy:1065
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_kit_5f350ad0:

#   "And with that Kit closed the door on me."
    "Y Kit me cerró la puerta."

# game/episode020.rpy:1072
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_b172b0af:

#   c "Any luck on the Petrarch situation?"
    c "¿Ha habido suerte con la situación de Petrarca?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1075
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_2fe1a88c:

#   j "No, master."
    j "No, amo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1077
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_0f2b2a80:

#   j "Not as of yet."
    j "Todavía no."

# game/episode020.rpy:1079
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_45390560:

#   j "There’s a lot of information on the situation."
    j "Hay mucha información sobre la situación."

# game/episode020.rpy:1080
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_3bc19472:

#   j "Most of it is propaganda or coverage on one of the many wars."
    j "La mayor parte es propaganda o cobertura de una de las muchas guerras."

# game/episode020.rpy:1081
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_cc1892bc:

#   j "It’s such a mess over there."
    j "Es un desastre allí."

# game/episode020.rpy:1082
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_a0030a0c:

#   c "Yes, Thyia already warned me."
    c "Sí, Thyia ya me lo advirtió."

# game/episode020.rpy:1083
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_30d4c75e:

#   c "No promising leads then?"
    c "¿No hay pistas prometedoras entonces?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1085
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_e7086021:

#   j "The easiest, or less complicated way for outsiders to make contact with any of the warring parties is when you can sell them weapons."
    j "La forma más fácil, o menos complicada, de que los forasteros entren en contacto con alguna de las partes enfrentadas es vendiéndoles armas."

# game/episode020.rpy:1086
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_fd2a736e:

#   c "I’m not that keen on delivering weapons of mass destruction, imaginary or not, just to get a meeting."
    c "No me entusiasma entregar armas de destrucción masiva, imaginarias o no, sólo para conseguir una reunión."

# game/episode020.rpy:1087
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_5b20fd1d:

#   j "I thought as much."
    j "Eso pensaba yo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1088
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_c921e25c:

#   c "What about appealing to any governments?"
    c "¿Y recurrir a algún gobierno?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1090
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_0023fccb:

#   j "There isn’t much in the way of government."
    j "No hay mucho gobierno."

# game/episode020.rpy:1092
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_bb012f6e:

#   j "Most of the planets are in a constant state of war and public offices are either corrupt or virtually non-existent."
    j "La mayoría de los planetas están en constante estado de guerra y los cargos públicos son corruptos o prácticamente inexistentes."

# game/episode020.rpy:1093
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_369cb35f:

#   c "Couldn’t we work with one of those corrupt governments?"
    c "¿No podríamos trabajar con uno de esos gobiernos corruptos?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1094
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_a41e0dc2:

#   c "Bribe our way through, or something?"
    c "¿Sobornarnos para pasar o algo así?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1096
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_8c375494:

#   j "Unlikely, making planet-side contact is very difficult."
    j "Poco probable, hacer contacto con el lado del planeta es muy difícil."

# game/episode020.rpy:1097
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_92de1b27:

#   j "Most of the habitable planets have military blockades around them, so getting through there is a big hurdle in itself."
    j "La mayoría de los planetas habitables tienen bloqueos militares a su alrededor, por lo que atravesarlos es un gran obstáculo en sí mismo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1098
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_e9e01ded:

#   j "And most terrestrial government offices have extremely limited power."
    j "Y la mayoría de las oficinas gubernamentales terrestres tienen un poder extremadamente limitado."

# game/episode020.rpy:1099
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_ab2cb593:

#   j "Most of the power is held by the most important branch economically speaking, meaning the military."
    j "La mayor parte del poder está en manos de la rama más importante económicamente hablando, es decir, el ejército."

# game/episode020.rpy:1100
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_08b6876c:

#   c "And the military is busy fighting wars in space?"
    c "¿Y los militares están ocupados librando guerras en el espacio?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1102
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_1186f752:

#   j "Yes, or slaughtering rivals on other planets."
    j "Sí, o masacrando rivales en otros planetas."

# game/episode020.rpy:1103
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_f5b79d86:

#   j "The power balance is heavily skewed in favor of the military, so contacting other ministries of any planet will likely get us nowhere."
    j "El equilibrio de poder está muy sesgado a favor del ejército, por lo que contactar con otros ministerios de cualquier planeta probablemente no nos lleve a ninguna parte."

# game/episode020.rpy:1104
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_31c04e56:

#   c "So, the military is only interested in weapons deals and the rest of politicians don’t have any meaningful influence."
    c "Así pues, a los militares sólo les interesan los negocios de armamento y el resto de los políticos no tienen ninguna influencia significativa."

# game/episode020.rpy:1106
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_7c01513a:

#   j "I’m afraid so."
    j "Me temo que sí."

# game/episode020.rpy:1107
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_8f08606f:

#   c "Thyia mentioned pirates?"
    c "¿Thyia mencionó a los piratas?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1109
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_6014b6da:

#   j "Yes, lots of piracy going on."
    j "Sí, hay mucha piratería."

# game/episode020.rpy:1110
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_9f3ad30a:

#   j "Sometimes the pirates even join the war, so there are several conflicts where planets are fighting against pirate bands."
    j "A veces los piratas incluso se unen a la guerra, por lo que hay varios conflictos en los que los planetas luchan contra bandas de piratas."

# game/episode020.rpy:1111
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_f3edb295:

#   c "Držić sounds like a more and more exhausting place by the minute."
    c "Držić parece un lugar cada vez más agotador por momentos."

# game/episode020.rpy:1113
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_0071a0af:

#   j "Not if you enjoy shooting and war crimes."
    j "No si te gustan los tiroteos y los crímenes de guerra."

# game/episode020.rpy:1114
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_f73d28a8:

#   c "Do you think any of those pirates would be a viable way to make contact and assure safe passing to Petrarch?"
    c "¿Crees que alguno de esos piratas sería una forma viable de establecer contacto y asegurar el paso a Petrarca?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1116
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_92713d00:

#   j "Maybe."
    j "Tal vez."

# game/episode020.rpy:1117
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_ca041837:

#   j "Most of the pirates have a terrible reputation."
    j "La mayoría de los piratas tienen una reputación terrible."

# game/episode020.rpy:1119
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_6198ad9b:

#   j "The ones made up out of deserters mostly just enjoy sowing chaos."
    j "Los formados por desertores en su mayoría sólo disfrutan sembrando el caos."

# game/episode020.rpy:1120
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_21cc6028:

#   j "There are a few that just want to make a living and operate under something approaching a code of honor."
    j "Hay algunos que sólo quieren ganarse la vida y operar bajo algo parecido a un código de honor."

# game/episode020.rpy:1121
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_d0c77953:

#   c "Honorable pirates, my favorite kind."
    c "Piratas honorables, mi tipo favorito."

# game/episode020.rpy:1124
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_d5b392e0:

#   j "I’m sure they’ll still steal and sell your firstborn child without any qualms."
    j "Seguro que seguirán robando y vendiendo a tu primogénito sin ningún reparo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1126
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_841ad650:

#   j "Don’t get your hopes up, I’m sure they’ll still steal and sell your firstborn child without any qualms."
    j "No te hagas ilusiones, seguro que siguen robando y vendiendo a tu primogénito sin ningún reparo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1127
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_bb503c7d:

#   c "But they’ll do it honorably..."
    c "Pero lo harán honorablemente..."

# game/episode020.rpy:1130
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_1ab09ac7:

#   j "Honor aside, would bounty hunting be something we could pursue?"
    j "Dejando a un lado el honor, ¿podríamos dedicarnos a la caza de recompensas?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1131
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_13251290:

#   c "Maybe."
    c "Tal vez."

# game/episode020.rpy:1133
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_ad5179a6:

#   j "Right."
    j "Bien."

# game/episode020.rpy:1134
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_e30f36b8:

#   j "Honor aside, how do you feel about bounty hunting?"
    j "Dejando a un lado el honor, ¿qué opinas de la caza de recompensas?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1135
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_eea6f4dd:

#   c "Ambivalent."
    c "Ambivalente."

# game/episode020.rpy:1137
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_396476c9:

#   j "One of the larger pirate groups, the Marleybone Irregulars, has posted a bounty on the boss of a rival gang."
    j "Uno de los grupos piratas más grandes, los Irregulares de Marleybone, ha puesto una recompensa por el jefe de una banda rival."

# game/episode020.rpy:1138
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_56f1eccf:

#   j "Apparently he ordered the murder of one of the higher-ups in the organization, one Captain Xile."
    j "Al parecer, ordenó el asesinato de uno de los altos cargos de la organización, un tal capitán Xile."

# game/episode020.rpy:1139
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_df236c1e:

#   j "The assassination was supposed to be discreet and made to look like an accident, to avoid suspicion and retaliation."
    j "El asesinato debía ser discreto y parecer un accidente, para evitar sospechas y represalias."

# game/episode020.rpy:1140
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_cf7c3b20:

#   j "The hit was botched, Xile lived to tell the tale and the Marleybone Irregulars were justifiably pissed off."
    j "El golpe fue una chapuza, Xile vivió para contarlo y los Irregulares de Marleybone estaban justificadamente cabreados."

# game/episode020.rpy:1141
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_adc3d4a3:

#   j "After the Irregulars interrogated the assassin, they found out about who was behind it."
    j "Después de que los Irregulares interrogaran al asesino, averiguaron quién estaba detrás."

# game/episode020.rpy:1142
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_2b5a9167:

#   j "Now they want him tracked down and killed."
    j "Ahora quieren localizarlo y matarlo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1143
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_2eabce6d:

#   j "I guess pirates aren’t big on fair trials."
    j "Supongo que a los piratas no les gustan los juicios justos."

# game/episode020.rpy:1144
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_1f148c6e:

#   c "Why don’t they do it themselves?"
    c "¿Por qué no lo hacen ellos mismos?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1147
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_738f9eba:

#   j "They’re too busy defending their territory, I think."
    j "Creo que están demasiado ocupados defendiendo su territorio."

# game/episode020.rpy:1149
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_94a7549f:

#   j "Too busy being pirates, I think."
    j "Demasiado ocupados siendo piratas, creo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1150
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_70fc21ee:

#   j "And everyone is keeping tabs on them, so no chance of a surprise attack on the rival gang’s headquarters."
    j "Y todo el mundo los vigila, así que no hay posibilidad de un ataque sorpresa a la sede de la banda rival."

# game/episode020.rpy:1151
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_15f8f1dc:

#   j "And according to their intel, the bounty is holed up with his gang just outside the boundaries of Držić."
    j "Y según su información, el cazarrecompensas está escondido con su banda justo fuera de los límites de Držić."

# game/episode020.rpy:1152
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_73dce076:

#   j "Probably out of fear of retaliation."
    j "Probablemente por miedo a represalias."

# game/episode020.rpy:1153
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_370b9b14:

#   c "The pirates don’t like to leave their home system?"
    c "¿A los piratas no les gusta salir de su sistema de origen?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1155
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_fe9f06e6:

#   j "Not in great numbers, I think they fear losing grip on their territory."
    j "No en gran número, creo que temen perder el control de su territorio."

# game/episode020.rpy:1156
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_15c9ede0:

#   c "So, we track down this rival pirate lord, hand him over to the pirates and ask for safe passage to Petrarch."
    c "Así que localizamos a este señor pirata rival, lo entregamos a los piratas y pedimos un salvoconducto a Petrarca."

# game/episode020.rpy:1159
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_a8bfd370:

#   j "That seems the best option to me, yes."
    j "Me parece la mejor opción, sí."

# game/episode020.rpy:1161
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_15e2af67:

#   j "Something like that, yeah."
    j "Algo así, sí."

# game/episode020.rpy:1162
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_4dced0ca:

#   j "The pirate band is large enough to offer some protection and they know the best routes through the system."
    j "La banda pirata es lo suficientemente grande como para ofrecer cierta protección y conocen las mejores rutas a través del sistema."

# game/episode020.rpy:1163
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_52583aa8:

#   c "We should set up a meet then, to arrange the terms."
    c "Deberíamos organizar una reunión entonces, para acordar los términos."

# game/episode020.rpy:1164
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_b924e403:

#   c "Can you set that up?"
    c "¿Puedes prepararlo?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1165
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_b56516a8:

#   j "Yes, I'll respond to the bounty notice."
    j "Sí, responderé al aviso de recompensa."

# game/episode020.rpy:1166
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_11c2ef05:

#   c "I'll discuss it with the others first."
    c "Lo discutiré primero con los demás."

# game/episode020.rpy:1167
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_5e4ace8e:

#   j "Of course."
    j "Por supuesto."

# game/episode020.rpy:1168
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_85d8e25d:

#   c "I guess we won't be the only ones responding to this notice?"
    c "Supongo que no seremos los únicos en responder a este aviso."

# game/episode020.rpy:1170
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_7c2bfcd6:

#   j "That's unlikely, I'm afraid."
    j "Eso es poco probable, me temo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1172
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_e9d551dd:

#   j "We could be lucky, but I think we should expect competition."
    j "Podríamos tener suerte, pero creo que deberíamos esperar competencia."

# game/episode020.rpy:1173
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_93ec9037:

#   j "The notice has been up for a while after all."
    j "Al fin y al cabo, el anuncio lleva tiempo publicado."

# game/episode020.rpy:1174
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_d59eccb5:

#   c "No reason to let this chance slip though."
    c "Sin embargo, no hay razón para dejar escapar esta oportunidad."

# game/episode020.rpy:1175
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_fe6b9cf0:

#   c "I'll let you know once we're ready to move."
    c "Te lo haré saber una vez que estemos listos para movernos."

# game/episode020.rpy:1195
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_0e5dc811:

#   "Several Bursts later, we arrived at the agreed spot."
    "Varias ráfagas más tarde, llegamos al lugar acordado."

# game/episode020.rpy:1196
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_1c088415:

#   "The Bastard’s scanners didn’t pick up any anomaly in the vicinity, so the pirates probably weren’t in the area yet."
    "Los escáneres del Bastardo no detectaron ninguna anomalía en las inmediaciones, así que probablemente los piratas aún no estaban en la zona."

# game/episode020.rpy:1198
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_459548d9:

#   "We waited for an hour, our apprehension growing by the minute."
    "Esperamos durante una hora, con una aprensión que crecía por momentos."

# game/episode020.rpy:1199
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_f9314571:

#   c "Not a very punctual lot, are they?"
    c "No son muy puntuales, ¿verdad?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1200
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_3fd05e6e:

#   ce "I don’t think pirates are known for that, to be honest."
    ce "No creo que los piratas sean conocidos por eso, para ser honesto."

# game/episode020.rpy:1201
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_047dda1d:

#   na "Not a very good first impression, I’d say."
    na "No es una muy buena primera impresión, diría yo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1202
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_858b968c:

#   c "I’m not sure they care very much."
    c "No estoy seguro de que les importe mucho."

# game/episode020.rpy:1203
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_c667e292:

#   ce "I’m picking up something!"
    ce "¡Estoy recogiendo algo!"

# game/episode020.rpy:1204
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_82df8b22:

#   ce "One contact approaching."
    ce "Se acerca un contacto."

# game/episode020.rpy:1206
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_d9b32120:

#   c "A large ship?"
    c "¿Un barco grande?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1207
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_f54bbecb:

#   ce "No, it appears to be a small shuttle."
    ce "No, parece ser un pequeño transbordador."

# game/episode020.rpy:1208
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_7e1c4391:

#   c "Less risk of getting shot to pieces then."
    c "Entonces hay menos riesgo de que te disparen."

# game/episode020.rpy:1209
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_850f436c:

#   av "Unless it’s a remote controlled bomb..."
    av "A menos que sea una bomba teledirigida..."

# game/episode020.rpy:1210
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_c73899f3:

#   ce "We’re being hailed."
    ce "Nos aclaman."

# game/episode020.rpy:1211
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_624bee8f:

#   c "Put them through."
    c "Pásalos."

# game/episode020.rpy:1214
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_187554cb:

#   man "Crew of the Iron Bastard, this shuttle has been sent to you courtesy of Captain Xile of the Marleybone Irregulars."
    man "Tripulación del Bastardo de Hierro, esta lanzadera les ha sido enviada por cortesía del Capitán Xile de los Irregulares de Marleybone."

# game/episode020.rpy:1215
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_05eb46ab:

#   man "Three members of your crew are to board this shuttle and they will be taken to Captain Xile at an undisclosed location."
    man "Tres miembros de su tripulación deben abordar esta lanzadera y serán llevados con el Capitán Xile a un lugar no revelado."

# game/episode020.rpy:1216
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_272bbdba:

#   man "Any attempt to track the shuttle will be met with appropriate violence and destruction of the shuttle."
    man "Cualquier intento de rastrear la lanzadera será respondido con la violencia apropiada y la destrucción de la lanzadera."

# game/episode020.rpy:1217
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_7ded2cdf:

#   man "After the audience with Captain Xile, the three crew members will be returned to you safely by means of the same shuttle."
    man "Tras la audiencia con el capitán Xile, los tres tripulantes serán devueltos sanos y salvos en la misma lanzadera."

# game/episode020.rpy:1218
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_558caa33:

#   man "Failure to board the shuttle will not result in any retaliatory action, but any subsequent petition of the Marleybone Irregulars will be categorically denied."
    man "El hecho de no subir a la lanzadera no dará lugar a represalias, pero cualquier petición posterior de los Irregulares de Marleybone será denegada categóricamente."

# game/episode020.rpy:1219
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_0b37dad8:

#   man "Message repeats."
    man "El mensaje se repite."

# game/episode020.rpy:1221
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_bffdedfa:

#   c "So it is a remote-controlled shuttle, just not an explosive one."
    c "Así que es una lanzadera teledirigida, pero no explosiva."

# game/episode020.rpy:1223
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_92931812:

#   av "Probably..."
    av "Probablemente..."

# game/episode020.rpy:1224
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_3dddde7a:

#   c "I guess we’ll need to board that shuttle then."
    c "Supongo que tendremos que abordar ese transbordador entonces."

# game/episode020.rpy:1225
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_68d8ce72:

#   c "Aven and Thyia, can you gear up and meet me at the airlock?"
    c "Aven y Thyia, ¿pueden equiparse y reunirse conmigo en la esclusa?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1226
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_d6cc5461:

#   av "Of course."
    av "Por supuesto."

# game/episode020.rpy:1228
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_e3f64a93:

#   "Céline allowed the shuttle to dock with the Bastard."
    "Céline permitió que la lanzadera se acoplara al Bastardo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1230
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_51bf26fe:

#   "Thyia and Aven were already at the airlock when I arrived."
    "Thyia y Aven ya estaban en la esclusa cuando llegué."

# game/episode020.rpy:1231
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_17a33c16:

#   c "Ready?"
    c "¿Preparado?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1232
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_77274c31:

#   av "Yes."
    av "Sí."

# game/episode020.rpy:1233
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_28f503fc:

#   th "Yup."
    th "Sí."

# game/episode020.rpy:1235
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_4ae17f2a:

#   "The airlock opened up and we stepped through the hatch into the shuttle."
    "La esclusa se abrió y entramos en la lanzadera."

# game/episode020.rpy:1236
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_1dace2f6:

#   "The confines of the craft were rather cramped, there was just enough room for three people."
    "El espacio de la nave era bastante reducido, apenas cabían tres personas."

# game/episode020.rpy:1237
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_defef755:

#   th "No chance of us getting comfortable, it seems."
    th "No hay posibilidad de que nos pongamos cómodos, parece."

# game/episode020.rpy:1238
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_47f003a1:

#   c "Doesn’t look like it."
    c "No lo parece."

# game/episode020.rpy:1240
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_9009c92f:

#   "The shuttle disengaged from the Bastard and began to sped along a pre-arranged route."
    "El transbordador se desacopló del Bastardo y comenzó a acelerar por una ruta preestablecida."

# game/episode020.rpy:1241
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_ba42faa3:

#   "Through the small windows in the shuttle, we could see the Bastard beginning to shrink out of view."
    "A través de las pequeñas ventanas de la lanzadera, pudimos ver cómo el Bastardo empezaba a encogerse hasta perderse de vista."

# game/episode020.rpy:1243
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_bb0b017c:

#   av "What’s that noise?"
    av "¿Qué es ese ruido?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1244
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_0c65b81b:

#   th "Noise?"
    th "¿Ruido?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1245
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_0ee4d1dd:

#   th "The engine you mean?"
    th "¿Te refieres al motor?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1246
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_9bd3e2d5:

#   av "No, whistling noise."
    av "No, ruido de silbidos."

# game/episode020.rpy:1247
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_c6000fe1:

#   c "It’s coming from these nozzles."
    c "Viene de estas boquillas."

# game/episode020.rpy:1248
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_9d4339f9:

#   c "Fuck, it’s some kind of gas."
    c "Joder, es algún tipo de gas."

# game/episode020.rpy:1250
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_2ac84699:

#   "There wasn’t enough time to panic as the gas rapidly spread in the small interior of the shuttle."
    "No hubo tiempo suficiente para que cundiera el pánico, ya que el gas se extendió rápidamente en el pequeño interior del transbordador."

# game/episode020.rpy:1251
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_482389ce:

#   "We were overwhelmed almost instantly and everything went dark."
    "Nos vimos desbordados casi al instante y todo se quedó a oscuras."

# game/episode020.rpy:1253
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_28df8047:

#   "The next time we opened our eyes, sunlight was streaming through the windows of the shuttle."
    "La siguiente vez que abrimos los ojos, la luz del sol entraba por las ventanillas de la lanzadera."

# game/episode020.rpy:1255
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_f0466ea0:

#   "We were still flying, but had entered the orbit of a planet some time ago."
    "Seguíamos volando, pero hacía tiempo que habíamos entrado en la órbita de un planeta."

# game/episode020.rpy:1256
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_37d85238:

#   "The gas must have induced an instantaneous sleep."
    "El gas debe haber inducido un sueño instantáneo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1257
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_e0e9a782:

#   "Thyia was the first to sit up."
    "Thyia fue la primera en incorporarse."

# game/episode020.rpy:1258
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_3864fffb:

#   th "Looks like the Irregulars take their security very seriously."
    th "Parece que los Irregulares se toman su seguridad muy en serio."

# game/episode020.rpy:1259
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_5485b1a2:

#   c "You think this is some kind of attempt to hide the location of their base from us?"
    c "¿Crees que es un intento de ocultarnos la ubicación de su base?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1260
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_ebb2a439:

#   th "I think so."
    th "Creo que sí."

# game/episode020.rpy:1261
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_80d85704:

#   c "As if we could plot a course to that base just by looking out of a tiny shuttle window."
    c "Como si pudiéramos trazar un rumbo a esa base con sólo mirar por la ventanilla de una minúscula lanzadera."

# game/episode020.rpy:1262
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_5ca47498:

#   th "I’m not saying it’s not an overblown security measure, just that it’s probably the reason for putting us to sleep."
    th "No digo que no sea una medida de seguridad exagerada, sólo que probablemente sea la razón para dormirnos."

# game/episode020.rpy:1264
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_bdad0bc7:

#   av "I have a fucking headache."
    av "Tengo un maldito dolor de cabeza."

# game/episode020.rpy:1265
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_bc80226a:

#   c "Me too, but we’re lucky that’s the only effect of the gas."
    c "Yo también, pero tenemos suerte de que ese sea el único efecto del gas."

# game/episode020.rpy:1267
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_b54c04bc:

#   "The shuttle was now apparently making its descent."
    "Al parecer, el transbordador estaba descendiendo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1268
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_47363900:

#   "We finally touched down in a clearing, near a large building looking very much like a bunker."
    "Finalmente aterrizamos en un claro, cerca de un gran edificio que se parecía mucho a un búnker."

# game/episode020.rpy:1269
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_6821bd83:

#   c "I think we’ve arrived."
    c "Creo que hemos llegado."

# game/episode020.rpy:1271
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_46cdf89f:

#   "The shuttle opened up and we were blinking against the light streaming down through the canopy of the forest."
    "El transbordador se abrió y parpadeamos contra la luz que se filtraba a través del dosel del bosque."

# game/episode020.rpy:1272
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_9c773d45:

#   "Several armed figures surrounded the shuttle."
    "Varias figuras armadas rodearon el transbordador."

# game/episode020.rpy:1274
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_3004d915:

#   woman "Come out slowly with your hands in the air."
    woman "Sal lentamente con las manos en alto."

# game/episode020.rpy:1275
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_d9f4b120:

#   "Considering the amount of guns trained on us, complying seemed like the best way to proceed."
    "Teniendo en cuenta la cantidad de armas apuntándonos, obedecer parecía la mejor manera de proceder."

# game/episode020.rpy:1276
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_010f0620:

#   woman "Follow me please."
    woman "Síganme, por favor."

# game/episode020.rpy:1277
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_79442ce0:

#   "No attempt was made to disarm us, the pirates were probably pretty confident in their strength in numbers."
    "No intentaron desarmarnos, probablemente los piratas confiaban en su fuerza numérica."

# game/episode020.rpy:1279
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_89e15e0b:

#   "The pirate who ordered us to come out of the shuttle led us toward the bunker."
    "El pirata que nos ordenó salir de la lanzadera nos condujo hacia el búnker."

# game/episode020.rpy:1280
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_7b9ea763:

#   "She motioned us inside after the large door opened."
    "Nos indicó que entráramos después de que se abriera la gran puerta."

# game/episode020.rpy:1282
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_f989e684:

#   "The inside of the bunker consisted of a single room crammed with storage containers, desks and various computer screens."
    "El interior del búnker consistía en una única habitación atestada de contenedores de almacenamiento, escritorios y varias pantallas de ordenador."

# game/episode020.rpy:1283
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_b8480bb8:

#   "The place didn’t really exude the glamour normally associated with pirate dens, no piles of lucre, crates filled with gold bars or even piles of illicit drugs on the many desks."
    "El lugar no desprendía el glamour que suele asociarse a las guaridas de piratas: no había montones de dinero, cajas llenas de lingotes de oro ni montones de drogas ilícitas sobre los numerosos escritorios."

# game/episode020.rpy:1284
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_e5987af2:

#   "The bunker mostly gave off an impression of a well-oiled intelligence office, which probably wasn’t far off the mark."
    "El búnker daba sobre todo la impresión de ser una oficina de inteligencia bien engrasada, lo que probablemente no estaba muy lejos de la realidad."

# game/episode020.rpy:1286
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_9b571380:

#   "A woman came into view."
    "Apareció una mujer."

# game/episode020.rpy:1287
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_92bdc41b:

#   "She was obviously a figure of authority, considering the way she was treated by all the people surrounding her."
    "Evidentemente, era una figura de autoridad, teniendo en cuenta la forma en que la trataba toda la gente que la rodeaba."

# game/episode020.rpy:1288
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_6e437cc7:

#   c "Captain Xile."
    c "Capitán Xile."

# game/episode020.rpy:1290
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_236b07db:

#   xi "You’re the bounty hunters."
    xi "Sois los cazarrecompensas."

# game/episode020.rpy:1291
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_237dc833:

#   "Her statement didn’t really sound like a question, so I kept silent, waiting for her to resume."
    "Su afirmación no sonó realmente como una pregunta, así que guardé silencio, esperando a que continuara."

# game/episode020.rpy:1292
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_0da26488:

#   xi "Are you prepared to kill Alilph Skeda for me?"
    xi "¿Estás dispuesto a matar a Alilph Skeda por mí?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1293
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_a62357ce:

#   c "He’s the mastermind behind the botched attempt on your life, I presume?"
    c "Es el autor intelectual del atentado frustrado contra tu vida, supongo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1294
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_f88220ce:

#   xi "He is."
    xi "Lo es."

# game/episode020.rpy:1295
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_83ffb970:

#   c "We will take him out."
    c "Lo sacaremos."

# game/episode020.rpy:1296
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_154ee49a:

#   xi "Excellent."
    xi "Excelente."

# game/episode020.rpy:1297
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_bdf0e24c:

#   xi "Our latest intel suggests he’s holed up with his crew, the Skivs, in his base on Aretine."
    xi "Nuestra última información sugiere que está escondido con su tripulación, los Skivs, en su base de Aretine."

# game/episode020.rpy:1298
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_584b5da2:

#   xi "I’ll leave the details of the operation to you, but beware that Aretine is a heavily fortified place."
    xi "Te dejaré los detalles de la operación a ti, pero ten cuidado que Aretine es un lugar fuertemente fortificado."

# game/episode020.rpy:1300
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_1578ecc4:

#   xi "I would not suggest a frontal assault."
    xi "Yo no sugeriría un asalto frontal."

# game/episode020.rpy:1301
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_b7f4b180:

#   c "Noted."
    c "Tomo nota."

# game/episode020.rpy:1302
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_1c2044ea:

#   c "May I asked why your organization hasn’t retaliated directly?"
    c "¿Puedo preguntarle por qué su organización no ha tomado represalias directamente?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1303
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_bf9edcb6:

#   c "From the little I’ve seen of your operation so far, you do not lack the manpower."
    c "Por lo poco que he visto de su operación hasta ahora, no les falta mano de obra."

# game/episode020.rpy:1305
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_8877923b:

#   xi "It’s not a question of manpower, nor of firepower."
    xi "No es una cuestión de mano de obra, ni de potencia de fuego."

# game/episode020.rpy:1307
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_70a29540:

#   xi "It’s politics, I’m afraid."
    xi "Es política, me temo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1309
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_a3162af5:

#   xi "Skeda’s gang has never officially claimed the attempt on my life, and an assault on Aretine by the Irregulars will surely be construed as an act of war."
    xi "La banda de Skeda nunca ha reclamado oficialmente el atentado contra mi vida, y un asalto a Aretine por parte de los Irregulares seguramente será interpretado como un acto de guerra."

# game/episode020.rpy:1310
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_9cc379a2:

#   xi "I don’t know if you are familiar with Držić and its environs, but there’s enough war already."
    xi "No sé si conoces Držić y sus alrededores, pero ya hay suficiente guerra."

# game/episode020.rpy:1311
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_8774c3a1:

#   xi "I do not wish to be an active participant in the armed conflict, it would be bad for business."
    xi "No deseo participar activamente en el conflicto armado, sería malo para el negocio."

# game/episode020.rpy:1312
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_89aefe22:

#   c "I see."
    c "Ya veo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1313
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_546f2481:

#   c "Posting a bounty doesn’t threaten any agreement between you and of the other gangs?"
    c "¿Poner una recompensa no amenaza ningún acuerdo entre tú y las otras bandas?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1315
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_7dc30270:

#   xi "I won’t bore you with the intricacies of gang politics, but let me assure you that it doesn’t."
    xi "No les aburriré con los entresijos de la política de bandas, pero permítanme asegurarles que no es así."

# game/episode020.rpy:1317
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_9943c204:

#   xi "If Skeda is killed as part of bounty collection, the bounty hunter nor the issuer will be met with hostilities from the other gangs."
    xi "Si Skeda es asesinado como parte del cobro de la recompensa, el cazarrecompensas ni el emisor se encontrarán con las hostilidades de las otras bandas."

# game/episode020.rpy:1318
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_aca43093:

#   xi "I can’t speak for the members of Skeda’s gang, of course, I’m sure they’ll be upset."
    xi "No puedo hablar por los miembros de la banda de Skeda, por supuesto, seguro que estarán disgustados."

# game/episode020.rpy:1319
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_58dca2ba:

#   c "I’m sure they will, but they’ll also be without a leader, so there’s bound to be some chaos."
    c "Estoy seguro de que lo harán, pero también se quedarán sin líder, así que seguro que habrá algo de caos."

# game/episode020.rpy:1320
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_61de6147:

#   xi "Exactly."
    xi "Exactamente."

# game/episode020.rpy:1321
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_ee7005ca:

#   xi "Now, I don’t know if you have done any prior research, but Aretine is a hostile planet."
    xi "Ahora, no sé si has hecho alguna investigación previa, pero Aretine es un planeta hostil."

# game/episode020.rpy:1322
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_9ab0d744:

#   xi "Volcanic, heavily polluted and a shithole in general really."
    xi "Volcánica, muy contaminada y una mierda en general."

# game/episode020.rpy:1323
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_05f2972d:

#   xi "A fitting home for a snake like Alilph Skeda."
    xi "Un hogar apropiado para una serpiente como Alilph Skeda."

# game/episode020.rpy:1324
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_82978a7d:

#   xi "We are willing to offer you some equipment to carry out an operation on Aretine."
    xi "Estamos dispuestos a ofrecerle algunos equipos para llevar a cabo una operación en Aretine."

# game/episode020.rpy:1325
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_87e7c622:

#   xi "If you are captured however, we will deny any involvement."
    xi "Sin embargo, si le capturan, negaremos cualquier implicación."

# game/episode020.rpy:1326
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_4e8c7062:

#   c "Of course."
    c "Por supuesto."

# game/episode020.rpy:1327
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_fd20e25a:

#   xi "Payment will occur after fulfilling the requirements of the bounty."
    xi "El pago se efectuará una vez cumplidos los requisitos de la recompensa."

# game/episode020.rpy:1328
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_1c4b43a8:

#   c "Yes, about that..."
    c "Sí, sobre eso..."

# game/episode020.rpy:1330
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_5caf6253:

#   xi "Let me make one thing clear, I will not haggle."
    xi "Voy a dejar una cosa clara, no voy a regatear."

# game/episode020.rpy:1331
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_e75f47a0:

#   c "We’re not interested in the money."
    c "No nos interesa el dinero."

# game/episode020.rpy:1333
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_2920ea96:

#   "That statement seemed to break Xile’s steely resolve just a fraction."
    "Esa afirmación pareció quebrantar un poco la férrea determinación de Xile."

# game/episode020.rpy:1334
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_4ce4dbda:

#   "She recovered almost immediately, but I knew I’d piqued her interest."
    "Se recuperó casi de inmediato, pero yo sabía que había despertado su interés."

# game/episode020.rpy:1336
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_2544f6f3:

#   xi "If you’re not interested in the money, that would make you the first bounty hunter in history to do so."
    xi "Si no le interesa el dinero, sería el primer cazarrecompensas de la historia en hacerlo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1337
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_74f5fb5b:

#   c "I’m flattered by the honor of being the first."
    c "Me halaga el honor de ser el primero."

# game/episode020.rpy:1338
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_e5b5f82a:

#   c "Instead of the cash reward, we would like a service rendered in return."
    c "En lugar de la recompensa en metálico, nos gustaría un servicio prestado a cambio."

# game/episode020.rpy:1339
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_234499cf:

#   xi "A service from the Marleybone Irregulars?"
    xi "¿Un servicio de los Marleybone Irregulars?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1340
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_26eefe0a:

#   c "Yes."
    c "Sí."

# game/episode020.rpy:1341
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_056dd648:

#   c "Držić is a very hostile environment, especially for single ships trying to get through the warzone unscathed."
    c "Držić es un entorno muy hostil, especialmente para las naves individuales que intentan atravesar la zona de guerra indemnes."

# game/episode020.rpy:1342
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_a7d03768:

#   c "We need to reach Petrarch."
    c "Tenemos que llegar a Petrarca."

# game/episode020.rpy:1343
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_96626039:

#   c "So, in return for killing Skeda, we’re asking you to provide us safe passage to Petrarch."
    c "Así que, a cambio de matar a Skeda, te pedimos que nos proporciones un pasaje seguro a Petrarca."

# game/episode020.rpy:1345
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_62b09fa9:

#   xi "Petrarch..."
    xi "Petrarca..."

# game/episode020.rpy:1347
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_6027f421:

#   xi "I’m sure you have your reasons for wanting to go there and I’m equally sure you’re not willing to divulge them."
    xi "Estoy seguro de que tiene sus razones para querer ir allí y estoy igualmente seguro de que no está dispuesto a divulgarlas."

# game/episode020.rpy:1348
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_e2051d0f:

#   c "That’s correct."
    c "Correcto."

# game/episode020.rpy:1349
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_b06c697a:

#   c "Is that a problem?"
    c "¿Es eso un problema?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1351
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_21ca17be:

#   xi "No."
    xi "No."

# game/episode020.rpy:1352
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_ad0728c9:

#   c "So do we have an agreement?"
    c "Entonces, ¿tenemos un acuerdo?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1353
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_66e65bad:

#   xi "Yes, we have."
    xi "Sí, lo hemos hecho."

# game/episode020.rpy:1354
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_4ccafe9d:

#   xi "In exchange for killing Alilph Skeda we will escort you through Držić to Petrarch."
    xi "A cambio de matar a Alilph Skeda te escoltaremos a través de Držić hasta Petrarca."

# game/episode020.rpy:1355
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_59db4782:

#   c "Good, consider it done then."
    c "Bien, considéralo hecho entonces."

# game/episode020.rpy:1356
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_b5de76c1:

#   xi "Contact us via the channel you’ve already used as soon as Skeda has been taken out."
    xi "Ponte en contacto con nosotros a través del canal que ya hayas utilizado en cuanto se haya retirado Skeda."

# game/episode020.rpy:1357
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_1f591ed9:

#   xi "We’ll arrange for a shuttle to pick you up."
    xi "Organizaremos un servicio de transporte para recogerle."

# game/episode020.rpy:1358
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_3e894e5d:

#   "Captain Xile turned on her heel and walked away, indicating our audience was officially over."
    "La capitana Xile giró sobre sus talones y se alejó, indicando que nuestra audiencia había terminado oficialmente."

# game/episode020.rpy:1374
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_274ae37a:

#   "The pirates took us back to the shuttle."
    "Los piratas nos llevaron de vuelta al transbordador."

# game/episode020.rpy:1375
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_7b314280:

#   c "Are we going to be drugged again?"
    c "¿Nos van a drogar otra vez?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1376
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_aa776053:

#   woman "Standard procedure."
    woman "Procedimiento estándar."

# game/episode020.rpy:1378
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_76b37c58:

#   "She didn’t elaborate any further and we were guided into the shuttle, the hatch closed and the gas started to fill the interior as soon as we took off."
    "No dio más explicaciones y nos guiaron hasta la lanzadera, la escotilla se cerró y el gas empezó a llenar el interior nada más despegar."

# game/episode020.rpy:1380
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_c2fc4bfd:

#   "We awoke when the shuttle had reached the Bastard again."
    "Nos despertamos cuando el transbordador había llegado de nuevo al Bastardo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1381
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_5fe6fb50:

#   "As soon as we’d docked and disembarked, the shuttle took off again."
    "En cuanto atracamos y desembarcamos, la lanzadera despegó de nuevo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1382
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_53ff03f7:

#   "We went on to get the crew up to speed on what we were about to do."
    "Pasamos a poner a la tripulación al corriente de lo que íbamos a hacer."

# game/episode020.rpy:1384
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_57bba659:

#   ce "As soon as the shuttle appeared on our scanners again, we got word about a drop-off point."
    ce "En cuanto la lanzadera volvió a aparecer en nuestros escáneres, nos informaron de un punto de descenso."

# game/episode020.rpy:1385
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_35a25ad2:

#   c "I think that’s the equipment Xile has promised us."
    c "Creo que es el equipo que Xile nos ha prometido."

# game/episode020.rpy:1386
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_953aca3a:

#   c "Let’s set a course to there first and then we’ll plan our approach to Aretine."
    c "Pongamos rumbo allí primero y luego planearemos nuestro acercamiento a Aretine."

# game/episode020.rpy:1388
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_6d7d3bdc:

#   "Travel to the location of the drop-off point took us one Burst."
    "El viaje hasta el punto de entrega nos llevó una ráfaga."

# game/episode020.rpy:1389
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_46f1b39c:

#   "The equipment turned out to be large containers holding two air speeders and a data package containing maps and environmental details of Aretine."
    "Los equipos resultaron ser grandes contenedores que contenían dos aceleradores aéreos y un paquete de datos con mapas y detalles medioambientales de Aretine."

# game/episode020.rpy:1391
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_635f3358:

#   "After hauling the containers into the cargo bay of the Bastard, Thyia quickly determined that the speeders were outfitted with reinforced armor plating."
    "Tras transportar los contenedores al hangar de carga del Bastard, Thyia comprobó rápidamente que los speeders estaban equipados con blindaje reforzado."

# game/episode020.rpy:1392
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_7ed6d970:

#   "The plating would probably be able to withstand the harsh conditions on Aretine Xile alluded to."
    "El chapado probablemente sería capaz de soportar las duras condiciones de Aretine a las que aludía Xile."

# game/episode020.rpy:1394
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_889b0ea3:

#   "The harshness of the planet were confirmed by Jade after accessing the data in the package."
    "La dureza del planeta fue confirmada por Jade tras acceder a los datos del paquete."

# game/episode020.rpy:1395
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_8c9d053d:

#   j "Aretine is covered in active volcanos and the atmosphere is constantly ravaged by firestorms."
    j "Aretine está cubierta de volcanes activos y la atmósfera está constantemente asolada por tormentas de fuego."

# game/episode020.rpy:1396
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_48cb658c:

#   j "You’d be mad to want to live there, but apparently Alilph Skeda thinks it’s the best place to live."
    j "Estarías loco si quisieras vivir allí, pero al parecer Alilph Skeda piensa que es el mejor lugar para vivir."

# game/episode020.rpy:1397
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_b9265385:

#   c "Or the place his enemies would think twice to attack."
    c "O el lugar donde sus enemigos se lo pensarían dos veces antes de atacar."

# game/episode020.rpy:1398
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_eb78bf27:

#   j "Skeda’s base is the only structure on the planet."
    j "La base de Skeda es la única estructura del planeta."

# game/episode020.rpy:1399
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_81dd759c:

#   j "It’s built in the middle of a lake of lava located in a basin that keeps most of it away from the foundations."
    j "Está construida en medio de un lago de lava situado en una cuenca que mantiene la mayor parte alejada de los cimientos."

# game/episode020.rpy:1400
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_5d01f126:

#   j "The entire base is covered in force fields to protect it against the elements."
    j "Toda la base está cubierta de campos de fuerza para protegerla de los elementos."

# game/episode020.rpy:1401
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_ac7469a8:

#   c "How do those speeders help us?"
    c "¿En qué nos ayudan esos velocípedos?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1403
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_bce35439:

#   th "As I said, they’re heavily plated and can operate in extreme temperatures."
    th "Como he dicho, están muy chapados y pueden funcionar a temperaturas extremas."

# game/episode020.rpy:1404
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_6f1b9edf:

#   c "Will our armor be able to withstand the heat?"
    c "¿Podrá nuestra armadura resistir el calor?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1405
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_b308ff0d:

#   th "Yes, that shouldn’t be a problem."
    th "Sí, eso no debería ser un problema."

# game/episode020.rpy:1406
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_613be504:

#   c "I guess Skeda has a lot of surveillance directly around his base."
    c "Supongo que Skeda tiene mucha vigilancia directamente alrededor de su base."

# game/episode020.rpy:1407
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_68d95923:

#   c "So we bring the Bastard down several miles away, unload the speeders and make our approach?"
    c "¿Así que bajamos al Bastardo a varias millas de distancia, descargamos los speeders y nos acercamos?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1408
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_c5c7e2b3:

#   c "Won’t they spot those speeders up anyway if we come too close?"
    c "¿No detectarán de todos modos a esos velocípedos si nos acercamos demasiado?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1409
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_1c53b2fd:

#   th "The speeders come equipped with a cloaking device."
    th "Los speeders vienen equipados con un dispositivo de camuflaje."

# game/episode020.rpy:1410
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_ead546a8:

#   c "Excellent."
    c "Excelente."

# game/episode020.rpy:1411
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_98a70507:

#   c "I just hope the element of surprise is enough."
    c "Sólo espero que el elemento sorpresa sea suficiente."

# game/episode020.rpy:1412
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_63b5635d:

#   c "Jade, I want you with me."
    c "Jade, te quiero conmigo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1413
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_fc7d8aba:

#   c "We’ll find a spot where you can infiltrate their network and take over some of the base operations."
    c "Encontraremos un lugar donde puedas infiltrarte en su red y tomar el control de algunas de las operaciones de la base."

# game/episode020.rpy:1414
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_6452058c:

#   c "I’m sure everyone in the base will be a lot more cooperative if we can switch off their force fields and sink the whole base into a river of lava at any point."
    c "Estoy seguro de que todos en la base serán mucho más cooperativos si podemos desactivar sus campos de fuerza y hundir toda la base en un río de lava en cualquier momento."

# game/episode020.rpy:1415
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_f02e56f4:

#   c "Aven and Kit will be on the other speeder."
    c "Aven y Kit estarán en el otro speeder."

# game/episode020.rpy:1416
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_bb2f2fe3:

#   c "The rest of the crew will wait on the Bastard for our signal to get us out of there."
    c "El resto de la tripulación esperará en el Bastardo nuestra señal para salir de allí."

# game/episode020.rpy:1417
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_367a2d8f:

#   th "There’s not much room for a contingency plan, is there?"
    th "No hay mucho margen para un plan de contingencia, ¿verdad?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1418
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_c11e0e67:

#   c "No, if the mission goes sideways the Bastard should go in, guns blazing, or leave without us."
    c "No, si la misión se tuerce el Bastardo debe entrar, disparando, o irse sin nosotros."

# game/episode020.rpy:1420
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_0473dcdf:

#   j "Let’s hope it doesn’t come to that."
    j "Esperemos no llegar a eso."

# game/episode020.rpy:1422
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_a557eb0c:

#   "Xile’s data included a relatively up to date overview of the conflicts in the area, allowing us to navigate through the turmoil."
    "Los datos de Xile incluían una visión relativamente actualizada de los conflictos en la zona, lo que nos permitió navegar a través de la agitación."

# game/episode020.rpy:1423
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_ed971aa5:

#   "Aretine was situated at the edge of the contested zone, so getting there wouldn’t be as difficult as reaching Petrarch."
    "Aretine estaba situada en el límite de la zona disputada, por lo que llegar hasta allí no sería tan difícil como alcanzar Petrarca."

# game/episode020.rpy:1424
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_81fcca50:

#   "Still, there was enough cause for discreetness, so Céline plotted a course that would take a roundabout way to Aretine."
    "Aun así, había motivos suficientes para la discreción, así que Céline trazó un rumbo que llevaría a Aretine por un camino indirecto."

# game/episode020.rpy:1430
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_89eb0283:

#   "We arrived some hours later and made our approach of the planet."
    "Llegamos unas horas más tarde y realizamos nuestra aproximación al planeta."

# game/episode020.rpy:1431
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_d8dc31d2:

#   "Xile hadn’t overstated the hostility of the planet."
    "Xile no había exagerado la hostilidad del planeta."

# game/episode020.rpy:1433
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_9014eac4:

#   "Multiple nearby smoking volcanoes polluted the air and a large flow of lava spread out like a river toward the horizon."
    "Múltiples volcanes humeantes cercanos contaminaban el aire y un gran flujo de lava se extendía como un río hacia el horizonte."

# game/episode020.rpy:1435
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_538f2691:

#   "The Bastard hovered above the boiling mass of stone as we deployed both speeders."
    "El Bastardo se cernía sobre la masa de piedra hirviente mientras desplegábamos los dos speeders."

# game/episode020.rpy:1436
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_6fa0abf6:

#   "Jade and me occupied one speeder, wearing our full protective suit and helmet."
    "Jade y yo ocupamos un speeder, con nuestro traje protector completo y casco."

# game/episode020.rpy:1437
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_70a2b158:

#   "Aven and Kit followed on the other speeder."
    "Aven y Kit les siguieron en el otro speeder."

# game/episode020.rpy:1438
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_e0475f18:

#   "Together we advanced on Skeda’s lair."
    "Juntos avanzamos hacia la guarida de Skeda."

# game/episode020.rpy:1439
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_b172a1c5:

#   "Our plan hinged on the intel Xile provided us with, so it’s safe to say I was a little apprehensive."
    "Nuestro plan dependía de la información que nos proporcionara Xile, así que no cabe duda de que me sentía un poco aprensivo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1440
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_f4522a3b:

#   "According to Xile, the environmental disturbances on Aretine were too massive for scanners to pick up smaller aircraft."
    "Según Xile, las perturbaciones ambientales en Aretine eran demasiado masivas para que los escáneres detectaran aeronaves más pequeñas."

# game/episode020.rpy:1441
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_b80b7a22:

#   "While a ship as large as the Bastard would be picked off by artillery on approach, something as small as a speeder would pass unnoticed."
    "Mientras que una nave tan grande como el Bastardo sería abatida por la artillería al acercarse, algo tan pequeño como un speeder pasaría desapercibido."

# game/episode020.rpy:1443
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_89270fd8:

#   "That left humanoid guards, which were supposedly very scarce, because of the harsh conditions on Aretine."
    "Quedaban los guardias humanoides, que supuestamente eran muy escasos, debido a las duras condiciones de Aretine."

# game/episode020.rpy:1444
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_a69385b3:

#   "Xile was pretty confident we could slip in unnoticed."
    "Xile estaba bastante seguro de que podríamos pasar desapercibidos."

# game/episode020.rpy:1445
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_d094dadd:

#   "Which led to me again to questioning why she hadn’t done so herself with a small covert strike team."
    "Lo que me llevó de nuevo a preguntarme por qué no lo había hecho ella misma con un pequeño equipo de ataque encubierto."

# game/episode020.rpy:1447
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_1440fd8c:

#   c "Man, this heat is killing me."
    c "Tío, este calor me está matando."

# game/episode020.rpy:1448
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_792967c8:

#   j "The suits shield us from most of it, but it sure is intense."
    j "Los trajes nos protegen de la mayor parte, pero es intenso."

# game/episode020.rpy:1449
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_66318614:

#   c "Ready to go?"
    c "¿Listo para salir?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1450
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_a423411c:

#   j "I am."
    j "Lo soy."

# game/episode020.rpy:1451
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_3cc7db1e:

#   av "Lead the way."
    av "Abre el camino."

# game/episode020.rpy:1453
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_06201bdb:

#   "Skeda’s base quickly appeared on the horizon, several towers contrasted against the smokey blood-red sky."
    "La base de Skeda apareció rápidamente en el horizonte, varias torres contrastaban con el cielo rojo sangre ahumado."

# game/episode020.rpy:1454
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_9d841063:

#   "It was the only structure in the vicinity, maybe even on the whole planet."
    "Era la única estructura en las inmediaciones, tal vez incluso en todo el planeta."

# game/episode020.rpy:1456
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_ceed5686:

#   "The artillery remained silent as we crossed the lava sea surrounding the base."
    "La artillería permaneció en silencio mientras cruzábamos el mar de lava que rodeaba la base."

# game/episode020.rpy:1457
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_2e1f3294:

#   "From our vantage point, the battlements appeared to be empty."
    "Desde nuestro punto de vista, las almenas parecían vacías."

# game/episode020.rpy:1458
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_f04ff387:

#   c "Let’s put the speeders down at the base of the building."
    c "Pongamos los speeders en la base del edificio."

# game/episode020.rpy:1460
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_6885301d:

#   av "Acknowledged."
    av "Reconocido."

# game/episode020.rpy:1462
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_60a4ab7c:

#   "We landed both our speeders in the shadow of one of the base’s towers."
    "Aterrizamos nuestros dos speeders a la sombra de una de las torres de la base."

# game/episode020.rpy:1464
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_ae81bc37:

#   ki "I think I saw movement up there, just when we landed."
    ki "Creo que vi movimiento allá arriba, justo cuando aterrizamos."

# game/episode020.rpy:1465
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_6a2be8c4:

#   c "Probably one of the guards."
    c "Probablemente uno de los guardias."

# game/episode020.rpy:1466
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_9019e012:

#   c "Only one way to find out for sure."
    c "Sólo hay una forma de saberlo con seguridad."

# game/episode020.rpy:1468
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_64c73fd1:

#   "By a series of ladders, we climbed up to the middle portions of the base."
    "Por una serie de escaleras, subimos a las partes centrales de la base."

# game/episode020.rpy:1469
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_294822bd:

#   "The only thing that could be heard on this floor were the broiling mass of lava beneath us and the hot wind whipping around the building."
    "Lo único que se oía en esta planta era la masa de lava ardiendo bajo nosotros y el viento caliente que azotaba el edificio."

# game/episode020.rpy:1470
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_0841c5f8:

#   c "Aven, Kit, you’re going round the other side, we’ll continue on."
    c "Aven, Kit, van por el otro lado, continuaremos."

# game/episode020.rpy:1471
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_53e87a5c:

#   av "Will do."
    av "Lo haré."

# game/episode020.rpy:1473
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_2a70b8b5:

#   "Just as we rounded the corner, Jade put an hand on my arm."
    "Justo cuando doblamos la esquina, Jade me puso una mano en el brazo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1475
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_e68766f6:

#   "She pointed at the mercenary standing on a platform further up ahead, his back turned."
    "Señaló al mercenario que estaba en una plataforma más adelante, de espaldas."

# game/episode020.rpy:1477
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_b8489778:

#   "The merc was facing the direction we had come from, so maybe he did spot something coming towards the base."
    "El mercenario estaba mirando en la dirección por la que habíamos venido, así que tal vez vio algo acercándose a la base."

# game/episode020.rpy:1482
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_8e3862c0:

#   "I indicated to Jade that we would sneak past him."
    "Le indiqué a Jade que nos escabulliríamos junto a él."

# game/episode020.rpy:1484
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_bca588bf:

#   "Just at that moment the mercenary turned towards us and whipped out his gun."
    "En ese momento, el mercenario se volvió hacia nosotros y sacó su pistola."

# game/episode020.rpy:1486
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_2efd8980:

#   man "Stop right there!"
    man "¡Alto ahí!"

# game/episode020.rpy:1488
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_deadcc86:

#   "As soon as he spoke those words, I rushed the merc while Jade fired upon him."
    "En cuanto dijo esas palabras, me abalancé sobre el mercenario mientras Jade disparaba contra él."

# game/episode020.rpy:1490
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_e1e0fb52:

#   "I narrowly avoided the merc’s blaster fire and threw myself bodily against him."
    "Evité por los pelos los disparos del mercenario y me lancé contra él."

# game/episode020.rpy:1491
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_bb0ac07a:

#   "The merc lost his balance while I skidded to a halt and steadied myself."
    "El mercenario perdió el equilibrio mientras yo patinaba y me estabilizaba."

# game/episode020.rpy:1493
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_1866941b:

#   "I could just see him topple over the edge and plunge to his certain death in the lava below."
    "Podía verle caer por el borde y precipitarse a una muerte segura en la lava."

# game/episode020.rpy:1497
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_10c021c8:

#   "Before he could turn towards us, I shot him in the back."
    "Antes de que pudiera volverse hacia nosotros, le disparé por la espalda."

# game/episode020.rpy:1499
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_33cf325d:

#   "The force of the blasts pushed him off the platform, plunging the merc to his death in the lava below."
    "La fuerza de las explosiones le empujó fuera de la plataforma, hundiendo al mercenario hasta su muerte en la lava."

# game/episode020.rpy:1500
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_01592faa:

#   c "I hope those shots didn’t alert any others."
    c "Espero que esos disparos no alertaran a nadie más."

# game/episode020.rpy:1501
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_723ae06e:

#   c "Let’s move."
    c "En marcha."

# game/episode020.rpy:1503
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_767fd86e:

#   "We met up with Aven and Kit on the other side of the building."
    "Nos reunimos con Aven y Kit al otro lado del edificio."

# game/episode020.rpy:1504
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_f7a19005:

#   ki "Any trouble?"
    ki "¿Algún problema?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1505
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_f5a8b940:

#   c "Some, but he’s taking a swim down below."
    c "Algunos, pero se está bañando abajo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1507
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_04ad4b6d:

#   ki "Ouch."
    ki "Ouch."

# game/episode020.rpy:1508
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_aea8754a:

#   av "This appears to be the entrance to the base."
    av "Esta parece ser la entrada a la base."

# game/episode020.rpy:1509
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_139c6bba:

#   c "Good."
    c "Bien."

# game/episode020.rpy:1510
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_20399da4:

#   c "In that case we’ll split up once again."
    c "En ese caso nos separaremos una vez más."

# game/episode020.rpy:1511
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_6847ce86:

#   c "Aven and Jade will find a way to tap into the main computer of the base."
    c "Aven y Jade encontrarán la forma de entrar en el ordenador central de la base."

# game/episode020.rpy:1512
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_fdda09cc:

#   c "See if you can find a way to disrupt the mercenary operations."
    c "A ver si encuentras la forma de desbaratar las operaciones mercenarias."

# game/episode020.rpy:1514
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_4500fbc9:

#   j "On it."
    j "En ello."

# game/episode020.rpy:1515
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_947d1f4c:

#   c "Kit, we’ll pay a visit to Skeda."
    c "Kit, haremos una visita a Skeda."

# game/episode020.rpy:1517
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_74ee1eec:

#   "Jade didn’t have to work on the door, as it just opened at the push of a button."
    "Jade no tuvo que trabajar en la puerta, ya que se abrió con sólo pulsar un botón."

# game/episode020.rpy:1518
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_b8d9a53d:

#   ki "Skeda really needs a lesson on domestic security."
    ki "Skeda realmente necesita una lección sobre seguridad doméstica."

# game/episode020.rpy:1519
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_13731ee3:

#   av "I guess he thinks the big guns and the lake of lava are enough protection."
    av "Supongo que piensa que las grandes armas y el lago de lava son suficiente protección."

# game/episode020.rpy:1520
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_1f06af48:

#   c "Well, we’re about to prove him wrong."
    c "Pues bien, estamos a punto de demostrarle que se equivoca."

# game/episode020.rpy:1522
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_9b74f299:

#   "Aven and Jade headed in the direction of where the base mainframe should be, while we made our way to the heart of the base."
    "Aven y Jade se dirigieron en dirección a donde debería estar el ordenador central de la base, mientras nosotros nos dirigíamos al corazón de la base."

# game/episode020.rpy:1524
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_d756039c:

#   "Just when I thought the base was deserted, we encountered two guards running toward us in a hallway."
    "Justo cuando pensaba que la base estaba desierta, nos encontramos con dos guardias que corrían hacia nosotros por un pasillo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1526
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_e073b115:

#   "We didn’t wait for them to draw on us and immediately fired on them."
    "No esperamos a que desenfundaran contra nosotros y les disparamos de inmediato."

# game/episode020.rpy:1528
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_4fef3df9:

#   "Kit caught the first one straight in the chest and the merc went down."
    "Kit alcanzó al primero directamente en el pecho y el mercenario cayó."

# game/episode020.rpy:1530
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_d4398ef8:

#   "The other merc tried to find cover behind several shipping containers, but I shot him in the head before he could get into position."
    "El otro mercenario intentó cubrirse detrás de varios contenedores, pero le disparé en la cabeza antes de que pudiera colocarse."

# game/episode020.rpy:1532
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_2b713afd:

#   ki "I guess they know we’ve arrived."
    ki "Supongo que saben que hemos llegado."

# game/episode020.rpy:1533
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_1221efcc:

#   c "I’m a little offended by the size of the welcoming party."
    c "Estoy un poco ofendido por el tamaño de la fiesta de bienvenida."

# game/episode020.rpy:1534
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_4ea66992:

#   ki "Be careful what you wish for."
    ki "Ten cuidado con lo que deseas."

# game/episode020.rpy:1536
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_33253495:

#   "As if on cue, four more mercs arrived."
    "Como si nada, llegaron cuatro mercenarios más."

# game/episode020.rpy:1537
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_804c717d:

#   "Kit and I dove behind the shipping containers and started firing from that position."
    "Kit y yo nos zambullimos detrás de los contenedores y empezamos a disparar desde esa posición."

# game/episode020.rpy:1539
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_b71bc8bb:

#   "One of the mercs was caught immediately in the crossfire."
    "Uno de los mercenarios quedó atrapado inmediatamente en el fuego cruzado."

# game/episode020.rpy:1540
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_5fe2431a:

#   "The others hunkered down at the corners of the intersection."
    "Los demás se agazaparon en las esquinas de la intersección."

# game/episode020.rpy:1541
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_84f4d889:

#   "For a couple of minutes, we exchanged fire."
    "Durante un par de minutos, intercambiamos disparos."

# game/episode020.rpy:1543
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_3cf1349d:

#   ki "This is so tedious."
    ki "Esto es muy tedioso."

# game/episode020.rpy:1544
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_92695614:

#   ki "Time to spice things up."
    ki "Es hora de animar las cosas."

# game/episode020.rpy:1546
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_b9ace9f4:

#   "Kit retrieved a grenade from his belt and lobbed it in the direction of the mercs."
    "Kit sacó una granada de su cinturón y la lanzó en dirección a los mercenarios."

# game/episode020.rpy:1548
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_fb95da55:

#   "There was some frantic shouting followed by a sharp bang."
    "Se oyeron unos gritos frenéticos seguidos de un golpe seco."

# game/episode020.rpy:1549
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_f47100b4:

#   "Kit and I sprang up immediately and started moving towards the intersection, firing into the cloud of smoke."
    "Kit y yo nos levantamos inmediatamente y empezamos a avanzar hacia la intersección, disparando contra la nube de humo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1551
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_39dc8c34:

#   "When the smoke dissipated we found the bodies of the remaining mercs among the rubble."
    "Cuando el humo se disipó, encontramos los cuerpos de los mercenarios restantes entre los escombros."

# game/episode020.rpy:1552
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_cbe23fd0:

#   av "We’re at the mainframe, encountered some resistance."
    av "Estamos en el ordenador central, encontramos algo de resistencia."

# game/episode020.rpy:1553
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_3fde4e19:

#   c "Us too, I think we’re near Skeda."
    c "Nosotros también, creo que estamos cerca de Skeda."

# game/episode020.rpy:1554
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_e9446c91:

#   c "Let me know when you’ve accessed the mainframe."
    c "Avísame cuando hayas accedido al ordenador central."

# game/episode020.rpy:1556
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_932bde5e:

#   "Kit and I ran in the direction of where the mercs had come from, until we reached a large door."
    "Kit y yo corrimos en la dirección de donde habían salido los mercenarios, hasta que llegamos a una gran puerta."

# game/episode020.rpy:1557
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_88d74e07:

#   "I punched the door controls and the double doors started sliding open."
    "Golpeé los mandos de la puerta y las puertas dobles empezaron a abrirse."

# game/episode020.rpy:1558
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_66a1577e:

#   "Any hopes of having reached the entrance to Skeda’s quarters were quickly dashed."
    "Cualquier esperanza de haber llegado a la entrada de los aposentos de Skeda se desvaneció rápidamente."

# game/episode020.rpy:1560
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_082bbf83:

#   "Instead, a bulky figure was revealed."
    "En su lugar, se reveló una figura voluminosa."

# game/episode020.rpy:1561
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_fbec8d78:

#   "Evidently belonging to the same species of frail-looking aliens we already encountered, this specimen was either a different breed or just freak of nature."
    "Evidentemente perteneciente a la misma especie de alienígenas de aspecto frágil que ya habíamos encontrado, este espécimen era de una raza diferente o simplemente un fenómeno de la naturaleza."

# game/episode020.rpy:1562
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_e0e91459:

#   ki "Oh fuck!"
    ki "¡Joder!"

# game/episode020.rpy:1564
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_b506e5fd:

#   "The muscled alien slammed Kit in the head with its weapon, causing him to crumple against the wall."
    "El musculoso alienígena golpeó a Kit en la cabeza con su arma, haciéndole desplomarse contra la pared."

# game/episode020.rpy:1566
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_b3777705:

#   "I managed to dart out of reach and fired several rounds of blaster fire which ricocheted against the merc’s armor."
    "Conseguí escabullirme y disparé varias ráfagas de blaster que rebotaron contra la armadura del mercenario."

# game/episode020.rpy:1567
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_57fee281:

#   "The guy was clearly enjoying himself as he lumbered towards me with murderous intent."
    "El tipo estaba claramente disfrutando mientras se acercaba a mí con intenciones asesinas."

# game/episode020.rpy:1569
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_e65c08d7:

#   man "Not so tough now, are you, human?"
    man "Ya no eres tan duro, ¿verdad, humano?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1570
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_63ec0dbd:

#   "I fired several more rounds into the merc, with each shot glancing off his armored suit."
    "Disparé varias veces más contra el mercenario, y cada disparo rebotó en su traje blindado."

# game/episode020.rpy:1571
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_6f66ff3e:

#   "His invincibility was starting to irritate me, so I frantically began to look for weak spots in his defences."
    "Su invencibilidad empezaba a irritarme, así que empecé a buscar frenéticamente puntos débiles en sus defensas."

# game/episode020.rpy:1572
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_772da4e1:

#   man "I’m going to have so much fun crushing you."
    man "Me voy a divertir mucho aplastándote."

# game/episode020.rpy:1573
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_c375a6b4:

#   c "Tell me, do those steroids you’re on slowly rot your brain or were you born stupid?"
    c "Dime, ¿esos esteroides que tomas te pudren lentamente el cerebro o naciste estúpido?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1575
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_cfa1147b:

#   "I was stalling for time, which appeared to be working, as the merc roared and rushed me."
    "Estaba ganando tiempo, y parecía que funcionaba, cuando el mercenario rugió y se abalanzó sobre mí."

# game/episode020.rpy:1576
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_6bc5c3cf:

#   man "I’ll teach the human some respect!"
    man "¡Le enseñaré algo de respeto al humano!"

# game/episode020.rpy:1578
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_abded885:

#   "I could only partly sidestep the giant’s blow and took his grazing fist partly in the stomach and everything briefly went black."
    "Sólo pude esquivar parcialmente el golpe del gigante y recibí su puño rozante parcialmente en el estómago y todo se volvió negro brevemente."

# game/episode020.rpy:1579
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_84e4406a:

#   "It took an Herculean effort not to double over and I nearly failed to duck from the armored fist aimed at my face."
    "Me costó un esfuerzo hercúleo no doblarme y estuve a punto de no esquivar el puño blindado que me apuntaba a la cara."

# game/episode020.rpy:1580
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_a44959c7:

#   "Apparently, the giant had decided to grind me down with his fists, a prospect that didn’t fill me with much enthusiasm."
    "Al parecer, el gigante había decidido machacarme con sus puños, una perspectiva que no me llenaba de mucho entusiasmo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1581
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_0d397059:

#   "Hitting him back was out of the question, the merc being encased in full armor."
    "Devolverle el golpe era imposible, ya que el mercenario llevaba una armadura completa."

# game/episode020.rpy:1582
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_8b785466:

#   "Still reeling with the after effects of the glancing blow, I kept looking for weak points in my opponent’s armor."
    "Todavía aturdido por los efectos del golpe de refilón, seguí buscando puntos débiles en la armadura de mi oponente."

# game/episode020.rpy:1583
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_75619cd0:

#   "Just then the merc lifted both his arms, ready to slam me down into the ground."
    "En ese momento, el mercenario levantó ambos brazos, dispuesto a estrellarme contra el suelo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1584
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_6b129ae0:

#   "That’s when I spotted the weak-looking padding in the area of his armpits."
    "Fue entonces cuando vi el acolchado de aspecto débil en la zona de sus axilas."

# game/episode020.rpy:1585
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_50e2a7d4:

#   "I had just one chance and not a whole lot of time to decide, so I took aim at one of the exposed armpits."
    "Sólo tenía una oportunidad y no mucho tiempo para decidirme, así que apunté a una de las axilas expuestas."

# game/episode020.rpy:1587
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_68f69a98:

#   "My shot hit home and penetrated the armor before the merc could lower his arms."
    "Mi disparo dio en el blanco y penetró la armadura antes de que el mercenario pudiera bajar los brazos."

# game/episode020.rpy:1588
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_40017639:

#   "The lumbering brute stood frozen and mute before me for several seconds as the blast of energy I’d fired traveled inside the armor."
    "El torpe bruto permaneció congelado y mudo ante mí durante varios segundos, mientras la ráfaga de energía que había disparado viajaba por el interior de la armadura."

# game/episode020.rpy:1589
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_79f62211:

#   "A roar of pain echoed throughout the hallway when the energy built up inside the merc’s protective shell and started cooking him inside it."
    "Un rugido de dolor resonó por todo el pasillo cuando la energía se acumuló dentro de la coraza protectora del mercenario y empezó a cocerlo dentro de ella."

# game/episode020.rpy:1591
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_c4573e2c:

#   "The merc flailed as blasts of fire sprouted from the seams at his arms."
    "El mercenario se agitó mientras ráfagas de fuego brotaban de las costuras de sus brazos."

# game/episode020.rpy:1592
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_ccf3ebca:

#   "Moments later, the head of the merc was engulfed in flames too."
    "Instantes después, la cabeza del mercenario también estaba envuelta en llamas."

# game/episode020.rpy:1594
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_c99f5791:

#   "The last of his screams died away as he toppled backwards and slammed onto the ground."
    "El último de sus gritos se apagó cuando cayó hacia atrás y se golpeó contra el suelo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1595
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_67e35a1b:

#   "I sidestepped the burning body to check on Kit, who stirred after being knocked against the wall."
    "Esquivé el cuerpo en llamas para ver cómo estaba Kit, que se agitaba tras ser golpeado contra la pared."

# game/episode020.rpy:1597
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_3fc15ae0:

#   c "Are you okay?"
    c "¿Se encuentra bien?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1598
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_d74e7511:

#   ki "Could be better, but I’ll live."
    ki "Podría ser mejor, pero viviré."

# game/episode020.rpy:1599
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_fe5cac72:

#   c "Ready to move on?"
    c "¿Listo para pasar página?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1600
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_bde6643a:

#   ki "Yup."
    ki "Sí."

# game/episode020.rpy:1601
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_ae51451f:

#   ki "I just hope that’s the only giant Skeda has hired to deal with intruders."
    ki "Sólo espero que sea el único gigante que Skeda haya contratado para hacer frente a los intrusos."

# game/episode020.rpy:1603
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_21bf70de:

#   "We made our way through the corridors was uncontested."
    "Nos abrimos paso por los pasillos sin oposición."

# game/episode020.rpy:1604
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_be25b9c2:

#   "Just as we reached the heart of Skeda’s base, Jade and Aven checked in again."
    "Justo cuando llegamos al corazón de la base de Skeda, Jade y Aven se registraron de nuevo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1605
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_2cc15622:

#   av "Jade has full access to the base mainframe."
    av "Jade tiene acceso total al ordenador central de la base."

# game/episode020.rpy:1606
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_704a4a9f:

#   av "She prevented the base from going on full alert."
    av "Evitó que la base entrara en alerta máxima."

# game/episode020.rpy:1607
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_0036bcea:

#   av "Most of the mercs were sleeping in the barracks, so she overrode the door controls and forced them to lock."
    av "La mayoría de los mercenarios dormían en los barracones, así que anuló los controles de las puertas y las obligó a cerrarse."

# game/episode020.rpy:1608
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_2fcf7665:

#   ki "Let’s hope no one wakes up then."
    ki "Esperemos que nadie se despierte entonces."

# game/episode020.rpy:1609
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_64bae172:

#   av "Unlikely, as the air filtration system is currently outputting a mixture of gasses that will knock out most known species."
    av "Es poco probable, ya que el sistema de filtración de aire emite actualmente una mezcla de gases que elimina la mayoría de las especies conocidas."

# game/episode020.rpy:1610
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_36af9bc7:

#   c "Good, that gives us a whole lot less to worry about."
    c "Bien, eso nos da mucho menos de qué preocuparnos."

# game/episode020.rpy:1611
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_2961912b:

#   c "Will she be able to cause some more damage?"
    c "¿Será capaz de causar más daño?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1612
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_7465c8b2:

#   av "I believe we can disable the heat shielding surrounding the entire base, leaving it unprotected."
    av "Creo que podemos desactivar el escudo térmico que rodea toda la base, dejándola desprotegida."

# game/episode020.rpy:1614
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_2db30970:

#   c "I assume the base wouldn’t last long without shields?"
    c "¿Supongo que la base no duraría mucho sin escudos?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1615
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_1b6f8418:

#   av "There were some reports stored on the base network containing projections of what would happen in case of a major outage."
    av "Había algunos informes almacenados en la red de la base que contenían proyecciones de lo que ocurriría en caso de un apagón importante."

# game/episode020.rpy:1616
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_cf8f496a:

#   av "Major structural damage to the buildings, electrical fires and explosions."
    av "Importantes daños estructurales en los edificios, incendios eléctricos y explosiones."

# game/episode020.rpy:1617
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_d07b69f6:

#   av "Without shields, the base wouldn’t last more than an hour."
    av "Sin escudos, la base no duraría más de una hora."

# game/episode020.rpy:1618
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_f4148b6d:

#   c "Excellent, now we just have to find Skeda."
    c "Excelente, ahora sólo tenemos que encontrar a Skeda."

# game/episode020.rpy:1619
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_dbeaf46a:

#   av "According to Jade, you’re nearing his location."
    av "Según Jade, estás cerca de su ubicación."

# game/episode020.rpy:1620
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_21482d9c:

#   c "That makes sense, considering the amount of firepower thrown at us for the past few minutes."
    c "Eso tiene sentido, teniendo en cuenta la cantidad de potencia de fuego lanzada contra nosotros en los últimos minutos."

# game/episode020.rpy:1621
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_7b4e9a10:

#   c "Be ready to trigger the chain reaction and make for the exit as soon as I give the signal."
    c "Prepárense para desencadenar la reacción en cadena y diríjanse a la salida en cuanto dé la señal."

# game/episode020.rpy:1622
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_b4ae8e70:

#   av "Understood."
    av "Entendido."

# game/episode020.rpy:1623
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_cf6b0c71:

#   c "Ready to have a word with Skeda?"
    c "¿Listo para hablar con Skeda?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1624
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_12309c29:

#   ki "Why don’t we just blow up the base right here and now?"
    ki "¿Por qué no volamos la base aquí y ahora?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1625
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_1ccb079c:

#   c "Tempting, but we have to make sure Skeda is actually here and make sure he doesn’t get a chance to leave."
    c "Tentador, pero tenemos que asegurarnos de que Skeda está realmente aquí y asegurarnos de que no tiene la oportunidad de irse."

# game/episode020.rpy:1626
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_98218a47:

#   ki "In that case, let’s find Skeda and give him the happy news."
    ki "En ese caso, busquemos a Skeda y démosle la feliz noticia."

# game/episode020.rpy:1628
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_782ac6ba:

#   "Skeda’s throne room was guarded by two mercs on full alert."
    "La sala del trono de Skeda estaba custodiada por dos mercenarios en alerta máxima."

# game/episode020.rpy:1629
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_51e1a998:

#   c "Don’t shoot, or you’ll regret it."
    c "No dispares o te arrepentirás."

# game/episode020.rpy:1630
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_f5ebd1ec:

#   c "We have some information your boss will want to hear."
    c "Tenemos información que su jefe querrá oír."

# game/episode020.rpy:1631
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_7c3896ca:

#   c "So I suggest you lower your weapons and take us to him."
    c "Así que sugiero que bajen sus armas y nos lleven hasta él."

# game/episode020.rpy:1632
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_90a17002:

#   "The guards hesitated, unsure what to do."
    "Los guardias dudaron, sin saber qué hacer."

# game/episode020.rpy:1633
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_f5120de8:

#   c "If you’re thinking of calling for backup, I wouldn’t bother."
    c "Si estás pensando en pedir refuerzos, yo no me molestaría."

# game/episode020.rpy:1634
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_6bd49c95:

#   c "We have full control over the essential systems."
    c "Tenemos pleno control sobre los sistemas esenciales."

# game/episode020.rpy:1635
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_bd5b2be8:

#   c "If you need a demonstration, I can ask to open a hard vacuum on the other side of that door you’re guarding."
    c "Si necesitas una demostración, puedo pedir que abran un vacío duro al otro lado de esa puerta que estás vigilando."

# game/episode020.rpy:1636
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_c0ed5191:

#   c "We’ll be happy to speak to the person next in charge after Skeda expires."
    c "Estaremos encantados de hablar con el siguiente responsable tras la expiración de Skeda."

# game/episode020.rpy:1638
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_8e772d3e:

#   "This got their attention and one of the guards opened the door."
    "Esto llamó su atención y uno de los guardias abrió la puerta."

# game/episode020.rpy:1639
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_ab068a80:

#   c "Lead the way."
    c "Abre el camino."

# game/episode020.rpy:1640
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_f1d0597b:

#   "The guards brought us into a room, stacked with containers and crates."
    "Los guardias nos condujeron a una sala llena de contenedores y cajas."

# game/episode020.rpy:1641
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_29a7adad:

#   "The walls were lined with empty tables and chairs."
    "Las paredes estaban llenas de mesas y sillas vacías."

# game/episode020.rpy:1642
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_ac3b107e:

#   "This was probably were most of the mercs hung out when they weren’t out raiding or, in this case, sleeping."
    "Probablemente era el lugar donde se reunían la mayoría de los mercenarios cuando no estaban haciendo incursiones o, en este caso, durmiendo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1644
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_54369814:

#   "At the far end of the room a large throne was installed among the cargo containers."
    "En el otro extremo de la sala había un gran trono instalado entre los contenedores de carga."

# game/episode020.rpy:1645
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_1ee4c39c:

#   "In front of the throne, two naked feline aliens sat on their knees, obviously at the beck and call of the large man sitting in front of them."
    "Frente al trono, dos alienígenas felinos desnudos estaban sentados de rodillas, obviamente a las órdenes del gran hombre sentado frente a ellos."

# game/episode020.rpy:1647
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_23ed7b96:

#   "Kit made the mercs walking in front of us lie on the floor with their hands behind their head."
    "Kit hizo que los mercenarios que caminaban delante de nosotros se tumbaran en el suelo con las manos detrás de la cabeza."

# game/episode020.rpy:1648
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_73e21e0c:

#   c "I assume you’re Alilph Skeda?"
    c "¿Supongo que eres Alilph Skeda?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1650
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_99d432b8:

#   sk "I am."
    sk "Lo soy."

# game/episode020.rpy:1651
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_ae950200:

#   sk "And who might you be?"
    sk "¿Y quién podría ser usted?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1652
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_026c04f8:

#   c "I’m the person currently controlling this base."
    c "Soy la persona que actualmente controla esta base."

# game/episode020.rpy:1653
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_9fbcfd58:

#   "Skeda pushed a button on a panel attached to his throne."
    "Skeda pulsó un botón en un panel adosado a su trono."

# game/episode020.rpy:1654
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_a7dc4620:

#   c "Don’t bother alerting your fellow Skivs, they’re locked up in the barracks."
    c "No te molestes en alertar a tus compañeros Skivs, están encerrados en los barracones."

# game/episode020.rpy:1655
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_23e94112:

#   sk "What do you want?"
    sk "¿Qué es lo que quieres?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1656
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_530a9bf6:

#   c "To kill you."
    c "Para matarte."

# game/episode020.rpy:1658
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_85f971fa:

#   sk "That bitch sent you, didn’t she?"
    sk "Esa perra te envió, ¿no?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1659
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_fc3a499e:

#   sk "Xile has had it in for me for years."
    sk "Xile me tiene manía desde hace años."

# game/episode020.rpy:1660
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_25c4e0d6:

#   c "Assassination attempts seem to have that effect on people."
    c "Los intentos de asesinato parecen tener ese efecto en la gente."

# game/episode020.rpy:1662
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_01a0238a:

#   sk "You’re hired help."
    sk "Eres personal contratado."

# game/episode020.rpy:1663
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_db6b26f0:

#   sk "Allow me to make an counter-offer to whatever Xile is promising you."
    sk "Permíteme hacer una contraoferta a lo que Xile te está prometiendo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1667
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_15e84c18:

#   c "I’m listening."
    c "Te escucho."

# game/episode020.rpy:1669
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_39fdc7cc:

#   sk "I’m sure Xile is promising you a lot of money?"
    sk "Seguro que Xile te promete mucho dinero."

# game/episode020.rpy:1670
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_7ce8fb33:

#   c "Maybe she is."
    c "Tal vez lo sea."

# game/episode020.rpy:1671
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_9602e8ea:

#   c "You’re going to offer me more, aren’t you?"
    c "Vas a ofrecerme más, ¿verdad?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1672
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_05b0ae20:

#   sk "How perceptive, you’ve done this before."
    sk "Qué perspicaz, ya has hecho esto antes."

# game/episode020.rpy:1673
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_2aadbc19:

#   sk "Let me cut to the chase."
    sk "Permítanme ir al grano."

# game/episode020.rpy:1674
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_68e23924:

#   sk "I’ll offer you twenty thousand credits to kill that bitch and blow her base sky high."
    sk "Te ofrezco veinte mil créditos por matar a esa zorra y volar su base por los aires."

# game/episode020.rpy:1675
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_90145f2c:

#   c "Twenty is barely more than Xile is offering us."
    c "Veinte es apenas más de lo que nos ofrece Xile."

# game/episode020.rpy:1676
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_0464c90a:

#   c "Make it forty and we have a deal."
    c "Que sean cuarenta y tenemos un trato."

# game/episode020.rpy:1678
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_5ce089d7:

#   sk "That’s outrageous!"
    sk "¡Esto es indignante!"

# game/episode020.rpy:1679
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_c43fb502:

#   sk "Twenty-five."
    sk "Veinticinco."

# game/episode020.rpy:1680
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_087201bb:

#   c "Thirty-five."
    c "Treinta y cinco."

# game/episode020.rpy:1682
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_4c266dbf:

#   sk "Twenty-seven."
    sk "Veintisiete."

# game/episode020.rpy:1683
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_49cee1ad:

#   c "Thirty and I want the same deal I had with Xile."
    c "Treinta y quiero el mismo trato que tuve con Xile."

# game/episode020.rpy:1684
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_1f354d89:

#   sk "What did she agree to?"
    sk "¿A qué accedió?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1685
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_34c39294:

#   c "She was to provide us with safe passage through Petrarch."
    c "Ella debía proporcionarnos un paso seguro a través de Petrarca."

# game/episode020.rpy:1686
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_b17c954c:

#   sk "What do you want on Petrarch?"
    sk "¿Qué quieres de Petrarca?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1687
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_2838c0b9:

#   c "That’s none of your business."
    c "Eso no es asunto tuyo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1688
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_ef569477:

#   sk "Fine."
    sk "Bien."

# game/episode020.rpy:1690
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_d012f113:

#   sk "Thirty-thousand credits and an armed escort to Petrarch."
    sk "Treinta mil créditos y una escolta armada para Petrarca."

# game/episode020.rpy:1694
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_258e705e:

#   c "No offence, but Xile’s operation seems a lot more professional than yours."
    c "No te ofendas, pero la operación de Xile parece mucho más profesional que la tuya."

# game/episode020.rpy:1695
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_65056bca:

#   c "I can’t just walk in there and shoot her through the head."
    c "No puedo entrar ahí y dispararle en la cabeza."

# game/episode020.rpy:1697
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_bf140077:

#   sk "I admit we’ve had a few minor setbacks the past few years, for which the Irregulars are to blame."
    sk "Admito que hemos tenido algunos pequeños contratiempos en los últimos años, de los que son culpables los Irregulares."

# game/episode020.rpy:1698
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_469a8cc9:

#   sk "My crew will be restored to it’s former glory, after the Irregulars have been dealt with."
    sk "Mi tripulación será restaurada a su antigua gloria, después de que los Irregulares hayan sido eliminados."

# game/episode020.rpy:1699
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_aac4d386:

#   sk "So we need to rely on cunning."
    sk "Así que tenemos que confiar en la astucia."

# game/episode020.rpy:1700
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_e06bb0c0:

#   c "Cunning..."
    c "Astuto..."

# game/episode020.rpy:1701
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_6a6fb5e4:

#   sk "As you might have noticed, the Irregulars are very tight on security."
    sk "Como habrás notado, los Irregulares son muy estrictos en materia de seguridad."

# game/episode020.rpy:1702
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_285af71f:

#   sk "Nobody knows where exactly their base is located."
    sk "Nadie sabe dónde se encuentra exactamente su base."

# game/episode020.rpy:1703
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_ffda5021:

#   sk "Even the few ex-members of Xile’s crew will not tell anyone, even under torture."
    sk "Incluso los pocos ex miembros de la tripulación de Xile no se lo dirán a nadie, ni siquiera bajo tortura."

# game/episode020.rpy:1704
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_4ea14f8f:

#   sk "So, what I’m proposing is that you’ll wear a tracker when you next meet Xile."
    sk "Así que, lo que propongo es que lleves un rastreador la próxima vez que te encuentres con Xile."

# game/episode020.rpy:1706
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_1734491f:

#   sk "As soon as we have a fix on the location, we’ll swoop in and bomb that base to oblivion."
    sk "En cuanto sepamos dónde está, bombardearemos la base hasta hacerla desaparecer."

# game/episode020.rpy:1707
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_98ff09a1:

#   c "Two tiny flaws in that plan of yours."
    c "Dos pequeños defectos en ese plan tuyo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1708
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_ab236046:

#   c "One is that they’ll be sure to scan or search for tracking devices."
    c "Una es que se asegurarán de escanear o buscar dispositivos de seguimiento."

# game/episode020.rpy:1709
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_19e684d4:

#   c "And two is that I’ll still be in that base you plan on reducing to rubble."
    c "Y dos es que aún estaré en esa base que planeas reducir a escombros."

# game/episode020.rpy:1711
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_b4f06fdb:

#   sk "You won’t be wearing that tracker on your person."
    sk "No llevarás ese rastreador encima."

# game/episode020.rpy:1712
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_4259001d:

#   sk "I’ve managed to get my hands on a bio-degradable tracker that can be ingested."
    sk "He conseguido un rastreador biodegradable que se puede ingerir."

# game/episode020.rpy:1713
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_347f96c1:

#   sk "The activation is time-delayed, so it shouldn’t be visible on any scanners before it is too late."
    sk "La activación es retardada, por lo que no debería ser visible en ningún escáner antes de que sea demasiado tarde."

# game/episode020.rpy:1714
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_c0f3263c:

#   sk "We only need to pinpoint your location once."
    sk "Sólo tenemos que localizar su ubicación una vez."

# game/episode020.rpy:1716
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_ba876c4e:

#   sk "So you can go in and out of the Irregulars base before we enter orbit."
    sk "Así podrás entrar y salir de la base de los Irregulares antes de entrar en órbita."

# game/episode020.rpy:1717
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_5238ab13:

#   c "What do I tell Xile once I’m inside?"
    c "¿Qué le digo a Xile una vez dentro?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1718
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_135a9089:

#   c "I’m sure she’ll demand proof of your death."
    c "Seguro que exigirá pruebas de tu muerte."

# game/episode020.rpy:1720
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_c6a5426e:

#   "Skeda snapped his fingers and one of the cat women sprang up in response."
    "Skeda chasqueó los dedos y una de las mujeres gato se levantó en respuesta."

# game/episode020.rpy:1721
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_5e6f594b:

#   sk "Get me that bag from the fridge, will you, pet?"
    sk "Tráeme esa bolsa de la nevera, ¿quieres, cariño?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1723
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_232e5a46:

#   "The naked woman scampered toward the bar and retrieved a large bag, which she dropped in front of my feet."
    "La mujer desnuda correteó hacia la barra y cogió una bolsa grande, que dejó caer delante de mis pies."

# game/episode020.rpy:1725
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_3d78811b:

#   sk "Inside is a severed head."
    sk "Dentro hay una cabeza cortada."

# game/episode020.rpy:1726
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_851e0609:

#   c "How nice."
    c "Qué bonito."

# game/episode020.rpy:1727
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_e6693598:

#   c "That doesn’t help me much, unless it’s your head, which seems a stretch."
    c "Eso no me ayuda mucho, a menos que sea tu cabeza, lo que parece exagerado."

# game/episode020.rpy:1728
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_1d0b8740:

#   sk "It’s the head from a clone who met his unfortunate early demise."
    sk "Es la cabeza de un clon que encontró su desafortunada muerte prematura."

# game/episode020.rpy:1729
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_103cb138:

#   sk "Genetically it’s indistinguishable from me."
    sk "Genéticamente es indistinguible de mí."

# game/episode020.rpy:1731
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_1109f6c4:

#   sk "I’d say that’s proof enough."
    sk "Yo diría que eso es prueba suficiente."

# game/episode020.rpy:1732
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_e8d9163f:

#   sk "Convince Xile I’m dead, wait for the tracker to activate and get the hell out of there."
    sk "Convence a Xile de que estoy muerto, espera a que se active el rastreador y lárgate de allí."

# game/episode020.rpy:1733
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_c3ee0c63:

#   sk "I’ll be waiting with the requested escort and the money."
    sk "Estaré esperando con la escolta solicitada y el dinero."

# game/episode020.rpy:1734
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_bf8b3b20:

#   c "Pleasure doing business."
    c "Un placer hacer negocios."

# game/episode020.rpy:1735
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_3a421a07:

#   sk "Likewise."
    sk "Lo mismo digo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1737
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_b540166d:

#   "Before we left the base, I received the tracker Skeda talked about."
    "Antes de salir de la base, recibí el rastreador del que habló Skeda."

# game/episode020.rpy:1738
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_d87be5a1:

#   "Together with the head, Kit and I made our way down to where the speeders were parked."
    "Junto con el jefe, Kit y yo nos dirigimos hacia donde estaban aparcados los speeders."

# game/episode020.rpy:1740
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_73fd0b47:

#   c "Change of plans."
    c "Cambio de planes."

# game/episode020.rpy:1741
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_e35c1a24:

#   av "Come again?"
    av "¿Otra vez?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1742
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_da465f6f:

#   c "Skeda made us a better offer."
    c "Skeda nos hizo una oferta mejor."

# game/episode020.rpy:1743
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_c55df7e5:

#   c "Meet us at the speeders and I’ll explain everything."
    c "Encuéntranos en los speeders y te lo explicaré todo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1744
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_10dfbd52:

#   "Jade and Aven were a little apprehensive about this turn of events."
    "Jade y Aven estaban un poco aprensivos ante este giro de los acontecimientos."

# game/episode020.rpy:1746
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_15593a9a:

#   "Their misgivings were drowned out by Kit’s enthusiasm of the fortune we were promised by Skeda."
    "Sus recelos quedaron ahogados por el entusiasmo de Kit ante la fortuna que nos prometía Skeda."

# game/episode020.rpy:1747
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_0cda2ac2:

#   "In the end, both women trusted my judgement and we went back to the Bastard to get the others up to speed."
    "Al final, ambas mujeres confiaron en mi criterio y volvimos al Bastardo para que los demás se pusieran al día."

# game/episode020.rpy:1749
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_bf20f1d9:

#   c "Good to know you’re desperate."
    c "Es bueno saber que estás desesperado."

# game/episode020.rpy:1750
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_75cda7f8:

#   sk "So you accept?"
    sk "¿Así que aceptas?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1759
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_c9512020:

#   "As soon as we were out of orbit, Céline messaged the Irregulars for another meetup."
    "En cuanto salimos de órbita, Céline envió un mensaje a los Irregulares para otro encuentro."

# game/episode020.rpy:1760
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_67daae75:

#   "They responded promptly and we were subjected to the same song and dance as before."
    "Respondieron rápidamente y nos sometieron a la misma cantinela que antes."

# game/episode020.rpy:1762
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_5518e9a4:

#   "Aven and Thyia were with me on the shuttle that took us to the base of the Irregulars."
    "Aven y Thyia iban conmigo en la lanzadera que nos llevó a la base de los Irregulares."

# game/episode020.rpy:1765
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_7e97b784:

#   "The shuttle landed in the clearing and we were greeted once again by a squad of mercenaries who took us to the base."
    "El transbordador aterrizó en el claro y fuimos recibidos de nuevo por un escuadrón de mercenarios que nos llevó a la base."

# game/episode020.rpy:1767
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_c461099c:

#   "Xile awaited us in the lobby of the base."
    "Xile nos esperaba en el vestíbulo de la base."

# game/episode020.rpy:1769
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_5a43d7b5:

#   xi "I hear you have caused quite the inferno back on Aretine."
    xi "He oído que has causado un infierno en Aretine."

# game/episode020.rpy:1770
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_d4fb81d5:

#   c "Who knew that molten rock and steel foundations were such a bad combination?"
    c "¿Quién iba a decir que la roca fundida y los cimientos de acero eran una combinación tan mala?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1771
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_00936b37:

#   c "Skeda has been taken care off."
    c "Skeda se ha hecho cargo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1772
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_36483ff8:

#   xi "So I've heard."
    xi "Eso he oído."

# game/episode020.rpy:1773
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_c20466be:

#   xi "My crew has already sifted through the wreckage and found some of Skeda's remains."
    xi "Mi tripulación ya ha rebuscado entre los restos y ha encontrado algunos de Skeda."

# game/episode020.rpy:1774
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_b2163ada:

#   xi "Some of his crew managed to escape and have been spreading the word of Skeda's downfall."
    xi "Algunos miembros de su tripulación lograron escapar y han difundido la noticia de la caída de Skeda."

# game/episode020.rpy:1775
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_4e1596ce:

#   xi "You have my thanks for handling this situation so adequately."
    xi "Le doy las gracias por haber manejado esta situación tan adecuadamente."

# game/episode020.rpy:1776
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_d1924a94:

#   xi "Three ships are waiting for you at the coordinates that will be sent to you shortly."
    xi "Tres naves le esperan en las coordenadas que se le enviarán en breve."

# game/episode020.rpy:1777
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_b83247da:

#   xi "They will provide safe passage to Petrarch."
    xi "Proporcionarán un pasaje seguro a Petrarca."

# game/episode020.rpy:1778
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_19eec105:

#   c "Thank you very much."
    c "Muchas gracias."

# game/episode020.rpy:1779
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_877fec46:

#   xi "Your actions will not be forgotten."
    xi "Sus acciones no serán olvidadas."

# game/episode020.rpy:1780
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_4cd73265:

#   xi "Consider the Marleybone Irregulars to be an ally if you should ever encounter us again."
    xi "Considera a los Irregulares de Marleybone como un aliado si vuelves a encontrarnos."

# game/episode020.rpy:1781
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_8f20f7fc:

#   c "I sure will."
    c "Seguro que sí."

# game/episode020.rpy:1783
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_29c3fd3d:

#   "We left Xile and headed back to the shuttle."
    "Dejamos a Xile y nos dirigimos al transbordador."

# game/episode020.rpy:1784
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_84d19317:

#   "After another forcibly induced slumber, we were back on the Bastard again."
    "Tras otro sueño inducido a la fuerza, estábamos de nuevo en el Bastard."

# game/episode020.rpy:1786
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_d2d953ee:

#   "Céline punched in the coordinates and we went out to find the Marleybone Irregulars escort."
    "Céline marcó las coordenadas y salimos en busca de la escolta de los Irregulares de Marleybone."

# game/episode020.rpy:1798
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_07654a3e:

#   "I ingested the capsule Skeda had given me right before boarding the shuttle."
    "Ingerí la cápsula que Skeda me había dado justo antes de subir a la lanzadera."

# game/episode020.rpy:1799
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_63e01fc8:

#   "If the mercenary boss had lied or miscalculated and the tracker would show up a scan, we’d probably be dead in a few minutes."
    "Si el jefe mercenario hubiera mentido o calculado mal y el rastreador mostrara un escáner, probablemente estaríamos muertos en unos minutos."

# game/episode020.rpy:1800
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_2e66f649:

#   "Dreading the thought of not waking up again, sleep overtook us all."
    "Temiendo no volver a despertar, el sueño nos venció a todos."

# game/episode020.rpy:1801
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_fe3b3e48:

#   "Either Skeda’s plan had worked, or a firing squad was waiting for us on the planet surface, but we all woke up without any alarms going off."
    "O bien el plan de Skeda había funcionado, o bien nos esperaba un pelotón de fusilamiento en la superficie del planeta, pero todos nos despertamos sin que sonara ninguna alarma."

# game/episode020.rpy:1806
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_b270f0b1:

#   "I threw the sack with Skeda’s cloned head in front of her feet."
    "Lancé el saco con la cabeza clonada de Skeda delante de sus pies."

# game/episode020.rpy:1808
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_c182e3e1:

#   xi "The scans of the shuttle picked up a gruesome anomaly."
    xi "Los escáneres de la lanzadera detectaron una espantosa anomalía."

# game/episode020.rpy:1809
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_f9cdbcf2:

#   xi "I guess that anomaly is now lying at my feet?"
    xi "¿Supongo que esa anomalía está ahora a mis pies?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1810
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_f5934984:

#   c "I didn’t know how firm you wanted his death proven, so I took his head."
    c "No sabía cuán firme querías que se probara su muerte, así que tomé su cabeza."

# game/episode020.rpy:1811
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_ec76f8a4:

#   xi "We’ll test the DNA."
    xi "Analizaremos el ADN."

# game/episode020.rpy:1812
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_9341fe39:

#   xi "If there’s a match in our databanks, we’ll contact you."
    xi "Si hay alguna coincidencia en nuestros bancos de datos, nos pondremos en contacto con usted."

# game/episode020.rpy:1813
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_e897fbb0:

#   c "Thank you."
    c "Gracias, señor."

# game/episode020.rpy:1815
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_c870c7a5:

#   "The mercs lead us back to the shuttle again."
    "Los mercenarios nos llevan de nuevo a la lanzadera."

# game/episode020.rpy:1816
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_948d0676:

#   "I just hoped the tracker had properly activated during my talk with Xile."
    "Sólo esperaba que el rastreador se hubiera activado correctamente durante mi charla con Xile."

# game/episode020.rpy:1817
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_1a01c839:

#   "Skeda had never told me if I could tell the tracker was active."
    "Skeda nunca me había dicho si podía saber que el rastreador estaba activo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1818
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_92e2c4e1:

#   "I got my answer as soon as the shuttle was about to break orbit."
    "Obtuve mi respuesta en cuanto la lanzadera estaba a punto de salir de órbita."

# game/episode020.rpy:1820
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_684b3aa4:

#   "Several unknown ships broke orbit and descended on the base, dropping bombs and laser fire from the sky."
    "Varias naves desconocidas rompieron la órbita y descendieron sobre la base, lanzando bombas y fuego láser desde el cielo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1821
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_f6f4f2f5:

#   "The Marleybone Irregulars were caught completely off-guard as was evident by their failure to get any air bound defence off the ground."
    "A los Marleybone Irregulars les pilló completamente desprevenidos, como quedó patente por su incapacidad para hacer despegar cualquier defensa aérea."

# game/episode020.rpy:1823
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_8b26a7e2:

#   "Suddenly the comms of the shuttle crackled."
    "De repente, los comunicadores de la lanzadera crepitaron."

# game/episode020.rpy:1824
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_dcd4d2a0:

#   "For an instant I was afraid that Xile had triggered some remote self-destruct mechanism."
    "Por un instante temí que Xile hubiera activado algún mecanismo de autodestrucción a distancia."

# game/episode020.rpy:1825
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_97e2f030:

#   "Instead, we were treated by just the venom of her words."
    "En lugar de eso, nos trataron sólo con el veneno de sus palabras."

# game/episode020.rpy:1826
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_37cad003:

#   xi "You miserable traitor!"
    xi "¡Miserable traidor!"

# game/episode020.rpy:1827
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_fd27ffba:

#   xi "I’ll hunt you down through the galaxy, I’ll-"
    xi "Te perseguiré por toda la galaxia, yo..."

# game/episode020.rpy:1829
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_59a44024:

#   "The abrupt cut-off of Xile’s communication coincided with an enormous explosion."
    "El corte brusco de la comunicación de Xile coincidió con una enorme explosión."

# game/episode020.rpy:1830
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_d5cc9be2:

#   "We left the planet’s atmosphere as the headquarters of the Marleybone Irregulars were reduced to cinders."
    "Abandonamos la atmósfera del planeta mientras el cuartel general de los Irregulares de Marleybone quedaba reducido a cenizas."

# game/episode020.rpy:1832
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_696a2557:

#   "Skeda's mercs took a good while raining fire upon Xile's operation."
    "Los mercenarios de Skeda tardaron un buen rato en hacer llover fuego sobre la operación de Xile."

# game/episode020.rpy:1833
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_f0317670:

#   "Just when I started to get a little worried Skeda had forgotten all about us, a command carrier hailed us."
    "Justo cuando empezaba a preocuparme un poco de que Skeda se hubiera olvidado de nosotros, un portaaviones de mando nos llamó."

# game/episode020.rpy:1835
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_5919f141:

#   sk "Many thanks for delivering that bitch Xile on a platter for us."
    sk "Muchas gracias por traernos a esa zorra de Xile en bandeja."

# game/episode020.rpy:1836
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_ca41989b:

#   sk "You'll find that the credits have already arrived in your account."
    sk "Verás que los créditos ya han llegado a tu cuenta."

# game/episode020.rpy:1837
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_4de04a7d:

#   "Jade nodded to confirm, her eyes wide with incredulity after seeing the amount."
    "Jade asintió para confirmarlo, con los ojos abiertos de incredulidad tras ver la cantidad."

# game/episode020.rpy:1838
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_c6306f6a:

#   sk "Three of my finest ships are ready to escort you to Petrarch."
    sk "Tres de mis mejores naves están listas para escoltarte a Petrarca."

# game/episode020.rpy:1839
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_22998edf:

#   sk "It's been a pleasure doing business with you."
    sk "Ha sido un placer hacer negocios con ustedes."

# game/episode020.rpy:1840
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_06671601:

#   sk "Skeda out."
    sk "Skeda fuera."

# game/episode020.rpy:1842
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_b758158b:

#   "Céline punched in the coordinates Skeda gave us and we went out to find the escort."
    "Céline marcó las coordenadas que nos dio Skeda y salimos en busca de la escolta."

# game/episode020.rpy:1803
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_7e97b784_1:

#   "The shuttle landed in the clearing and we were greeted once again by a squad of mercenaries who took us to the base."
    "El transbordador aterrizó en el claro y fuimos recibidos de nuevo por un escuadrón de mercenarios que nos llevó a la base."

# game/episode020.rpy:1805
translate spanish ep020_pirate_rendevous_c461099c_1:

#   "Xile awaited us in the lobby of the base."
    "Xile nos esperaba en el vestíbulo de la base."

# game/episode020.rpy:1857
translate spanish ep020_aretine_skeda_kill_d4d36915:

#   c "Not really interested."
    c "No me interesa."

# game/episode020.rpy:1858
translate spanish ep020_aretine_skeda_kill_f3316c4e:

#   c "Besides, if I betray Xile, I’ll have the entire contingent of Irregulars out for my blood."
    c "Además, si traiciono a Xile, tendré a todo el contingente de Irregulares buscando mi sangre."

# game/episode020.rpy:1860
translate spanish ep020_aretine_skeda_kill_a50a2225:

#   "Skeda got up from his throne suddenly, incandescent with rage."
    "Skeda se levantó de golpe de su trono, incandescente de rabia."

# game/episode020.rpy:1862
translate spanish ep020_aretine_skeda_kill_1380d310:

#   "Both Kit and I fired immediately and the mercenary leader slumped back into his high-backed chair."
    "Tanto Kit como yo disparamos inmediatamente y el líder mercenario se desplomó en su silla de respaldo alto."

# game/episode020.rpy:1864
translate spanish ep020_aretine_skeda_kill_a69f12d4:

#   sk "You shot me, you miserable motherfucker!"
    sk "¡Me disparaste, miserable hijo de puta!"

# game/episode020.rpy:1865
translate spanish ep020_aretine_skeda_kill_34f291fb:

#   "One of our shots must have hit home, because Skeda was bleeding from the mouth and breathing with some difficulty."
    "Uno de nuestros disparos debió de dar en el blanco, porque Skeda sangraba por la boca y respiraba con cierta dificultad."

# game/episode020.rpy:1866
translate spanish ep020_aretine_skeda_kill_b8ba008d:

#   sk "I’ll hunt you down!"
    sk "¡Te cazaré!"

# game/episode020.rpy:1867
translate spanish ep020_aretine_skeda_kill_f2f12cbc:

#   sk "I’ll-"
    sk "Yo..."

# game/episode020.rpy:1869
translate spanish ep020_aretine_skeda_kill_ff85bd76:

#   "With that last statement, the light went out in his eyes."
    "Con esa última afirmación, la luz se apagó en sus ojos."

# game/episode020.rpy:1871
translate spanish ep020_aretine_skeda_kill_1260536b:

#   c "Aven, let’s blow up this base."
    c "Aven, volemos esta base."

# game/episode020.rpy:1872
translate spanish ep020_aretine_skeda_kill_0b56763d:

#   c "Make sure that the procedure is irreversible, but allow any evacuation attempts."
    c "Asegúrese de que el procedimiento es irreversible, pero permita cualquier intento de evacuación."

# game/episode020.rpy:1873
translate spanish ep020_aretine_skeda_kill_ca117560:

#   av "On it."
    av "En ello."

# game/episode020.rpy:1874
translate spanish ep020_aretine_skeda_kill_46f4f0d0:

#   av "Jade is unlocking the crew quarters as well, the fresh air and alarms should wake those sleeping mercs right up."
    av "Jade también está abriendo las habitaciones de la tripulación, el aire fresco y las alarmas deberían despertar a esos mercenarios dormidos."

# game/episode020.rpy:1876
translate spanish ep020_aretine_skeda_kill_6ab60dc9:

#   "Moments later, alarms began to sound everywhere, warning the inhabitants of the base of a critical power failure."
    "Momentos después, las alarmas empezaron a sonar por todas partes, avisando a los habitantes de la base de un fallo crítico de energía."

# game/episode020.rpy:1877
translate spanish ep020_aretine_skeda_kill_a65f4f4d:

#   "The feline women were the first to run, followed by the guards hitherto lying on the ground by our command."
    "Las mujeres felinas fueron las primeras en correr, seguidas por los guardias que hasta entonces yacían en el suelo por orden nuestra."

# game/episode020.rpy:1879
translate spanish ep020_aretine_skeda_kill_7c57d830:

#   "Kit and I made for the exit as well."
    "Kit y yo también nos dirigimos a la salida."

# game/episode020.rpy:1880
translate spanish ep020_aretine_skeda_kill_b050c610:

#   "Whatever Jade had done, it caused a general panic."
    "Sea lo que sea lo que Jade había hecho, causó un pánico general."

# game/episode020.rpy:1882
translate spanish ep020_aretine_skeda_kill_55c27a3e:

#   "Mercs were running through the corridors, not even looking at us as we ran along."
    "Los mercenarios corrían por los pasillos sin mirarnos."

# game/episode020.rpy:1883
translate spanish ep020_aretine_skeda_kill_4e4f3af0:

#   "There was a general scramble towards the base hangars, where the aircraft would take some of the mercs to safety."
    "Hubo un tumulto general hacia los hangares de la base, donde los aviones llevarían a algunos de los mercenarios a un lugar seguro."

# game/episode020.rpy:1885
translate spanish ep020_aretine_skeda_kill_4099fe9d:

#   "Aven and Jade met up with us at the base of the building where our speeders were still waiting for us."
    "Aven y Jade se reunieron con nosotros en la base del edificio, donde aún nos esperaban nuestros speeders."

# game/episode020.rpy:1886
translate spanish ep020_aretine_skeda_kill_4e666ab2:

#   "Due to the collapse of the base shields, the lava now had free reign and was spilling over the foundations of the base."
    "Debido al colapso de los escudos de la base, la lava tenía ahora vía libre y se derramaba sobre los cimientos de la base."

# game/episode020.rpy:1887
translate spanish ep020_aretine_skeda_kill_9ce09acd:

#   "The buildings were creaking and groaning as the heat eroded the concrete."
    "Los edificios crujían y gemían a medida que el calor erosionaba el hormigón."

# game/episode020.rpy:1888
translate spanish ep020_aretine_skeda_kill_ac796daf:

#   c "No time to waste, let’s get back to the Bastard."
    c "No hay tiempo que perder, volvamos al Bastardo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1889
translate spanish ep020_aretine_skeda_kill_fa2e367b:

#   av "Is Skeda dead?"
    av "¿Ha muerto Skeda?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1890
translate spanish ep020_aretine_skeda_kill_e87c500b:

#   c "He is."
    c "Lo es."

# game/episode020.rpy:1891
translate spanish ep020_aretine_skeda_kill_65a0bb43:

#   ki "About to go down with his beautiful base."
    ki "A punto de caer con su hermosa base."

# game/episode020.rpy:1892
translate spanish ep020_aretine_skeda_kill_f6f64b79:

#   j "How are we going to prove to Xile that Skeda is actually dead?"
    j "¿Cómo vamos a demostrar a Xile que Skeda está realmente muerto?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1893
translate spanish ep020_aretine_skeda_kill_ace7cd60:

#   c "I think Xile will do a sweep of the planet and sift through the wreckage of the base."
    c "Creo que Xile hará un barrido del planeta y buscará entre los restos de la base."

# game/episode020.rpy:1894
translate spanish ep020_aretine_skeda_kill_d2577f34:

#   c "And a lot of the merc have already escaped, I’m sure they have some exciting tales to tell about Skeda’s demise."
    c "Y muchos de los mercenarios ya han escapado, seguro que tienen historias emocionantes que contar sobre la desaparición de Skeda."

# game/episode020.rpy:1896
translate spanish ep020_aretine_skeda_kill_0f016bae:

#   "We flew our speeders back to the Bastard, as portions of the base started to explode behind us."
    "Volamos en nuestros speeders de vuelta al Bastardo, mientras partes de la base empezaban a explotar a nuestras espaldas."

# game/episode020.rpy:1903
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_e173ca52:

#   "Jade was waiting for me in the lobby of the medical center."
    "Jade me esperaba en el vestíbulo del centro médico."

# game/episode020.rpy:1904
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_17a33c16:

#   c "Ready?"
    c "¿Preparado?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1906
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_7b4c5bc7:

#   j "Absolutely."
    j "Absolutamente."

# game/episode020.rpy:1907
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_890f157c:

#   j "I’m so happy we’re doing this."
    j "Me alegro mucho de que hagamos esto."

# game/episode020.rpy:1908
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_e0224be1:

#   c "Me too."
    c "A mí también."

# game/episode020.rpy:1909
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_dcd34462:

#   "A nurse came for us and escorted Jade and me to the room we would be occupying for the duration of the procedure."
    "Una enfermera vino a buscarnos y nos acompañó a Jade y a mí a la habitación que ocuparíamos durante la intervención."

# game/episode020.rpy:1911
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_e5d62d3c:

#   "We had a moment to ourselves when she left to fetch the doctor."
    "Tuvimos un momento para nosotros cuando se fue a buscar al médico."

# game/episode020.rpy:1912
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_bce52649:

#   c "Since I’m only getting an injection, do you think I’ll be allowed to stay for your operation?"
    c "Como sólo me van a poner una inyección, ¿cree que podré quedarme a su operación?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1914
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_083f4540:

#   j "You’re probably not allowed to stay in the same room."
    j "Probablemente no te permitan quedarte en la misma habitación."

# game/episode020.rpy:1915
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_bdf47131:

#   c "I’ll wait outside for you then."
    c "Te esperaré fuera entonces."

# game/episode020.rpy:1916
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_c93376a5:

#   j "I’d appreciate that."
    j "Te lo agradecería."

# game/episode020.rpy:1918
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_9e873f62:

#   "The nurse came back and I got the injection without much preamble."
    "La enfermera volvió y me pusieron la inyección sin muchos preámbulos."

# game/episode020.rpy:1919
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_63cb4ec4:

#   "The doctor declared me fit to leave immediately."
    "El médico me declaró apto para salir inmediatamente."

# game/episode020.rpy:1921
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_7cfd80b3:

#   c "That sure was quick."
    c "Eso sí que fue rápido."

# game/episode020.rpy:1922
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_11d10732:

#   c "I hope yours is as quick and painless as well."
    c "Espero que la suya también sea tan rápida e indolora."

# game/episode020.rpy:1923
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_b377bca7:

#   j "I hope so too."
    j "Yo también lo espero."

# game/episode020.rpy:1924
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_c02bfc48:

#   c "Take care, Jade, I’ll be waiting outside."
    c "Cuídate, Jade, estaré esperando afuera."

# game/episode020.rpy:1925
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_f134e22c:

#   c "I love you."
    c "Te quiero."

# game/episode020.rpy:1927
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_b6b100ad:

#   j "I love you too."
    j "Yo también te quiero."

# game/episode020.rpy:1929
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_3da374c5:

#   "I sat on a bench in the adjoining corridor and waited for the nurse to come get me."
    "Me senté en un banco del pasillo contiguo y esperé a que la enfermera viniera a buscarme."

# game/episode020.rpy:1930
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_6126afc8:

#   "My mind wandered, and suddenly I was gripped by fear that the procedure would be plagued by complications."
    "Mi mente divagaba y, de repente, me asaltó el miedo a que el procedimiento estuviera plagado de complicaciones."

# game/episode020.rpy:1931
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_918839c9:

#   "Jade had told me that the intervention was relatively safe, but what if she’d downplayed the risks?"
    "Jade me había dicho que la intervención era relativamente segura, pero ¿y si había restado importancia a los riesgos?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1932
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_fff42ac2:

#   "I knew now how badly she wanted to get pregnant, what if she’d presented me with only half of the facts?"
    "Ahora sabía lo mucho que deseaba quedarse embarazada, ¿y si me hubiera presentado sólo la mitad de los hechos?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1933
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_bfb5b750:

#   "Jade had proved herself to be an honest person, time and time again, especially with me."
    "Jade había demostrado ser una persona honesta, una y otra vez, especialmente conmigo."

# game/episode020.rpy:1934
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_8089d34c:

#   "But what if love had made her blind to the risks?"
    "Pero, ¿y si el amor la hubiera hecho ciega a los riesgos?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1935
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_e620d676:

#   "These panicky and rather unhelpful thoughts occupied me for much of the wait."
    "Estos pensamientos de pánico y poco útiles me ocuparon durante gran parte de la espera."

# game/episode020.rpy:1937
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_267bab69:

#   "After less than an hour, the nurse came out of Jade’s room and beckoned me."
    "Al cabo de menos de una hora, la enfermera salió de la habitación de Jade y me hizo señas."

# game/episode020.rpy:1939
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_943e7919:

#   woman "The procedure was a success, she asked for you as soon as she woke up."
    woman "El procedimiento fue un éxito, preguntó por ti en cuanto se despertó."

# game/episode020.rpy:1941
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_45309dc5:

#   "I entered the room and was met by Jade, propped up on the bed, wearing a radiant smile."
    "Entré en la habitación y me encontré con Jade, apoyada en la cama, con una sonrisa radiante."

# game/episode020.rpy:1942
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_15454135:

#   j "The doctor said that it was a success!"
    j "El médico dijo que había sido un éxito."

# game/episode020.rpy:1943
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_61deb00b:

#   c "So I’ve heard."
    c "Eso he oído."

# game/episode020.rpy:1944
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_31626ce1:

#   c "How do you feel?"
    c "¿Cómo te sientes?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1946
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_ffd3fb72:

#   j "A little groggy, but otherwise nothing but happiness."
    j "Un poco aturdido, pero por lo demás nada más que felicidad."

# game/episode020.rpy:1947
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_4448d179:

#   c "Good!"
    c "¡Bien!"

# game/episode020.rpy:1948
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_b939a83a:

#   c "We’re going to make this work, aren’t we?"
    c "Vamos a hacer que esto funcione, ¿verdad?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1949
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_6ad7c5ba:

#   j "We sure are!"
    j "¡Claro que sí!"

# game/episode020.rpy:1950
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_dc4dc6cb:

#   c "When are you allowed to leave?"
    c "¿Cuándo puedes irte?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1952
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_da367f03:

#   j "They need to do some final checkups and then we’re free to leave."
    j "Tienen que hacer algunas revisiones finales y luego podremos irnos."

# game/episode020.rpy:1953
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_c85bd76b:

#   j "I can’t wait to get into bed with you!"
    j "¡No puedo esperar a meterme en la cama contigo!"

# game/episode020.rpy:1954
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_bb979c77:

#   c "Wow, you’re not one for half-measures, are you?"
    c "Vaya, no te gustan las medias tintas, ¿verdad?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1956
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_689fc659:

#   j "You know me!"
    j "¡Ya me conoces!"

# game/episode020.rpy:1957
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_8e853cb5:

#   j "But unfortunately we have to wait for a few days, because of the procedure..."
    j "Pero por desgracia tenemos que esperar unos días, debido al procedimiento..."

# game/episode020.rpy:1958
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_34cdc001:

#   c "In that case we’ll wait a few days and go at it like rabbits afterwards."
    c "En ese caso esperaremos unos días y seguiremos como conejos después."

# game/episode020.rpy:1960
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_c2b5e91c:

#   j "That’s a deal!"
    j "¡Trato hecho!"

# game/episode020.rpy:1961
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_6b998bbf:

#   "Jade and I waited for the final tests."
    "Jade y yo esperamos las pruebas finales."

# game/episode020.rpy:1963
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_240a2501:

#   "After she was cleared, we both left the medical wing and headed back to the residential area."
    "Cuando le dieron el visto bueno, ambos salimos del ala médica y nos dirigimos a la zona residencial."

# game/episode020.rpy:1965
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_91c15237:

#   "Back in my room we went to bed immediately, both yearning to celebrate the moment by just being together."
    "De vuelta en mi habitación, nos fuimos a la cama inmediatamente, ambos deseando celebrar el momento simplemente estando juntos."

# game/episode020.rpy:1967
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_fbb98e50:

#   "Jade and I soon fell asleep and didn’t wake until the following morning."
    "Jade y yo nos dormimos pronto y no nos despertamos hasta la mañana siguiente."

# game/episode020.rpy:1969
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_jade_procedure_41610092:

#   "The day was filled with other obligations, so we parted ways making solemn vows to plan several nights of debauchery to mark our mutual fertility..."
    "El día estaba repleto de otras obligaciones, así que nos separamos haciendo votos solemnes para planear varias noches de desenfreno con motivo de nuestra mutua fertilidad..."

# game/episode020.rpy:1974
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_04c8250e:

#   "I’d discussed the matter of Thim wanting to stay on Paclerara with most of the crew in the past few days."
    "En los últimos días había comentado con la mayoría de la tripulación que Thim quería quedarse en Paclerara."

# game/episode020.rpy:1975
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_8e71edb9:

#   "Most of the people who didn’t know him from the Academy said they would trust the judgement of the people who knew him best."
    "La mayoría de las personas que no le conocían de la Academia dijeron que confiarían en el juicio de las personas que le conocían mejor."

# game/episode020.rpy:1978
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_a72ee2e3:

#   "So I gathered my sisters, Céline and Kit to settle the matter."
    "Así que reuní a mis hermanas, Céline y Kit para arreglar el asunto."

# game/episode020.rpy:1980
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_932c7809:

#   "So I gathered Eva, Lilly, Céline and Kit to settle the matter."
    "Así que reuní a Eva, Lilly, Céline y Kit para arreglar el asunto."

# game/episode020.rpy:1982
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_9c2de20d:

#   ki "Our boy wants to leave, does he?"
    ki "Nuestro chico quiere irse, ¿verdad?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1983
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_a76c75ed:

#   c "He doesn’t feel he’s of much use as a crew member and wants to stay here."
    c "No cree que sea muy útil como miembro de la tripulación y quiere quedarse aquí."

# game/episode020.rpy:1984
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_5dc096d9:

#   ki "Well, he sure isn’t of much use, that’s for sure."
    ki "Bueno, seguro que no es de mucha utilidad, eso seguro."

# game/episode020.rpy:1986
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_d7635e98:

#   ce "Kit..."
    ce "Kit..."

# game/episode020.rpy:1988
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_bbecb8de:

#   ki "What?"
    ki "¿Cómo?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1989
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_a331eba3:

#   ki "We hated the guy’s guts for our entire stay at the Academy."
    ki "Odiamos a ese tipo durante toda nuestra estancia en la Academia."

# game/episode020.rpy:1991
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_bd21e03a:

#   ce "I know, but we did take him against his will."
    ce "Lo sé, pero nos lo llevamos contra su voluntad."

# game/episode020.rpy:1992
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_24623a0d:

#   ki "Only because he was about to get the guards and ruin our escape."
    ki "Sólo porque estaba a punto de atrapar a los guardias y arruinar nuestro escape."

# game/episode020.rpy:1993
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_9ff1b83a:

#   c "All true, of course."
    c "Todo cierto, por supuesto."

# game/episode020.rpy:1994
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_2ea6e291:

#   c "Do we think he’s less of a threat now?"
    c "¿Creemos que ahora es menos amenazador?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1996
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_ef21c3ae:

#   l "Less of a threat in a sense that he won’t try to betray us again?"
    l "¿Menos amenaza en el sentido de que no intentará traicionarnos de nuevo?"

# game/episode020.rpy:1997
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_26eefe0a:

#   c "Yes."
    c "Sí."

# game/episode020.rpy:1998
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_76047705:

#   l "He had quite a few opportunities in the recent past and didn’t take them."
    l "Tuvo bastantes oportunidades en el pasado reciente y no las aprovechó."

# game/episode020.rpy:2000
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_0362e1b6:

#   e "He could have raised the alarm at any of the stations we were docked."
    e "Podría haber dado la alarma en cualquiera de las estaciones en las que estábamos atracados."

# game/episode020.rpy:2001
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_d3647ff5:

#   ce "True."
    ce "Cierto."

# game/episode020.rpy:2002
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_9ce5798f:

#   ce "I’ve never liked him much and he hasn’t made any effort to socialize with any of us, but I can’t blame him really."
    ce "Nunca me ha caído muy bien y no ha hecho ningún esfuerzo por socializar con ninguno de nosotros, pero la verdad es que no puedo culparle."

# game/episode020.rpy:2004
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_c55e104c:

#   ki "Well, if we’re all going to be rational about it, I can’t blame him either."
    ki "Bueno, si todos vamos a ser racionales al respecto, tampoco puedo culparle."

# game/episode020.rpy:2005
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_7cd61ac4:

#   ki "Not anymore, at least."
    ki "Al menos, ya no."

# game/episode020.rpy:2006
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_dc29f6b7:

#   c "So do we allow him to stay on Paclerara?"
    c "¿Le permitimos quedarse en Paclerara?"

# game/episode020.rpy:2008
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_7550fd40:

#   l "What’s he going to do here?"
    l "¿Qué va a hacer aquí?"

# game/episode020.rpy:2009
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_24ed7344:

#   c "Get some menial job, probably, something under the radar."
    c "Conseguir algún trabajo servil, probablemente, algo bajo el radar."

# game/episode020.rpy:2010
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_eefb9f10:

#   e "He’s not going back to the Sovereignty?"
    e "¿No va a volver a la Soberanía?"

# game/episode020.rpy:2011
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_d10cf3cf:

#   c "I don’t see that happening, to be honest."
    c "No creo que eso ocurra, la verdad."

# game/episode020.rpy:2013
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_4d9cd8d3:

#   ki "I’m sure they’ll have plenty of questions for him if he does, none of them friendly."
    ki "Estoy seguro de que tendrán muchas preguntas para él si lo hace, ninguna de ellas amistosa."

# game/episode020.rpy:2015
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_9ded53a7:

#   ce "The Sovereignty isn’t known for their welcoming disposition."
    ce "La Soberanía no es conocida por su talante acogedor."

# game/episode020.rpy:2017
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_3779821b:

#   ki "We’re sure we don’t want to use him as bait, a human shield or just a punching bag?"
    ki "¿Estamos seguros de que no queremos utilizarlo como cebo, escudo humano o simple saco de boxeo?"

# game/episode020.rpy:2020
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_4a6cad76:

#   c "Who’s in favor of letting him go?"
    c "¿Quién está a favor de dejarle marchar?"

# game/episode020.rpy:2021
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_0054f605:

#   ce "I am."
    ce "Lo soy."

# game/episode020.rpy:2023
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_6b51495e:

#   l "Me too."
    l "A mí también."

# game/episode020.rpy:2025
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_06059743:

#   e "Yes, me too."
    e "Sí, yo también."

# game/episode020.rpy:2027
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_cf47fa32:

#   ki "I guess I don’t mind either way."
    ki "Supongo que no me importa de cualquier manera."

# game/episode020.rpy:2028
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_91230dce:

#   c "That’s settled then."
    c "Eso está arreglado entonces."

# game/episode020.rpy:2029
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_f11940e3:

#   c "I’ll let him know."
    c "Se lo haré saber."

# game/episode020.rpy:2030
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_02fd69c0:

#   ki "I’m going to miss that silent brooding presence in my peripheral vision at future crew meetings."
    ki "Voy a echar de menos esa presencia silenciosa y melancólica en mi visión periférica en las futuras reuniones de la tripulación."

# game/episode020.rpy:2031
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_1a5cb9a4:

#   c "I’m sure you’ll get over your aching sense of loss."
    c "Estoy seguro de que superarás tu dolorosa sensación de pérdida."

# game/episode020.rpy:2033
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_c73a3637:

#   "I left to find Thim and met up with him on the observation deck."
    "Salí en busca de Thim y me reuní con él en la plataforma de observación."

# game/episode020.rpy:2034
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_dda16456:

#   c "Can I have a word?"
    c "¿Podemos hablar?"

# game/episode020.rpy:2036
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_b31b912c:

#   t "Of course."
    t "Por supuesto."

# game/episode020.rpy:2037
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_8a830ef9:

#   c "I’ve discussed your request with the rest of the crew."
    c "He discutido su petición con el resto de la tripulación."

# game/episode020.rpy:2038
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_8c2b2d37:

#   c "They’re agreeing to let you go, on the condition that you won’t try to contact the Sovereignty and keep a low profile."
    c "Están de acuerdo en dejarte ir, con la condición de que no intentes contactar con el Soberano y mantengas un perfil bajo."

# game/episode020.rpy:2040
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_119e2224:

#   t "That’s good news."
    t "Son buenas noticias."

# game/episode020.rpy:2042
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_69dacfe9:

#   t "And don’t worry, I’m not going back to the Sovereignty."
    t "Y no te preocupes, no voy a volver a la Soberanía."

# game/episode020.rpy:2043
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_374ceda1:

#   t "There’s nothing for me there anymore."
    t "Ya no hay nada para mí allí."

# game/episode020.rpy:2044
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_ec7ccb82:

#   t "I want to try my luck somewhere else."
    t "Quiero probar suerte en otro sitio."

# game/episode020.rpy:2045
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_a297fe64:

#   c "Well, you’re free to do so."
    c "Eres libre de hacerlo."

# game/episode020.rpy:2046
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_e1969452:

#   c "Good luck, Thim."
    c "Buena suerte, Thim."

# game/episode020.rpy:2048
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_b94712ed:

#   t "Thank you, [p_name]."
    t "Gracias, [p_name]."

# game/episode020.rpy:2049
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_b0dfa1c9:

#   t "I’ll make sure my bunk is empty before you depart from Paclerara."
    t "Me aseguraré de que mi litera esté vacía antes de que salgas de Paclerara."

# game/episode020.rpy:2051
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_3d9e6915:

#   "We shook hands and I took my leave of Thim."
    "Nos dimos la mano y me despedí de Thim."

# game/episode020.rpy:2052
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_7b722f4b:

#   "Him and I would never have become friends, but parting ways like this was the most amicable way we could have resolved things between us."
    "Él y yo nunca habríamos llegado a ser amigos, pero separarnos así era la forma más amistosa de resolver las cosas entre nosotros."

# game/episode020.rpy:2019
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_thim_d7635e98_1:

#   ce "Kit..."
    ce "Kit..."

# game/episode020.rpy:2059
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_428050bc:

#   "I was sitting on a bench near the landing pads in the midday sunlight of Paclerara, a steady stream of people passing me by."
    "Estaba sentado en un banco cerca de las pistas de aterrizaje, a la luz del sol del mediodía de Paclerara, con un flujo constante de gente que pasaba a mi lado."

# game/episode020.rpy:2060
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_7a4c7a59:

#   "Paclerara was a modestly busy spaceport, attracting the inevitable traders, but also a good amount of tourists."
    "Paclerara era un puerto espacial modestamente concurrido, que atraía a los inevitables comerciantes, pero también a una buena cantidad de turistas."

# game/episode020.rpy:2062
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_8757eccd:

#   "Raene found me observing the crowd and sat down next to me."
    "Raene me encontró observando a la multitud y se sentó a mi lado."

# game/episode020.rpy:2064
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_e631b5fd:

#   ra "Hey [p_name_short]."
    ra "Hola [p_name_short]."

# game/episode020.rpy:2065
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_0bc14a9d:

#   c "Hey, did you come out here to enjoy the sun as well?"
    c "Oye, ¿tú también has venido a disfrutar del sol?"

# game/episode020.rpy:2067
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_56c54b0f:

#   ra "Yes, I just went for a swim."
    ra "Sí, acabo de ir a nadar."

# game/episode020.rpy:2068
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_2c543d70:

#   ra "It seems like another great day out here."
    ra "Parece otro gran día aquí."

# game/episode020.rpy:2070
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_af92a25e:

#   ra "But I hear we're going to leave this place soon?"
    ra "¿Pero he oído que vamos a dejar este lugar pronto?"

# game/episode020.rpy:2071
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_659ae768:

#   c "Yes, we have a lead."
    c "Sí, tenemos una pista."

# game/episode020.rpy:2072
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_b7fd9a0a:

#   c "Thyia and Jade are looking at our options."
    c "Thyia y Jade están estudiando nuestras opciones."

# game/episode020.rpy:2073
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_9e433e85:

#   c "But it's looking like it's going to be a dangerous undertaking."
    c "Pero parece que va a ser una empresa peligrosa."

# game/episode020.rpy:2074
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_391b2b5e:

#   ra "That's not something new, is it?"
    ra "No es algo nuevo, ¿verdad?"

# game/episode020.rpy:2075
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_97ca0b98:

#   c "I guess not."
    c "Supongo que no."

# game/episode020.rpy:2077
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_c20c81eb:

#   ra "Best we enjoy this beautiful place a little while longer."
    ra "Es mejor que disfrutemos de este hermoso lugar un poco más."

# game/episode020.rpy:2080
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_6dc83d68:

#   "Raene took my hand and we sat together in silence, watching the crowd shuffle past in both directions."
    "Raene me cogió de la mano y nos sentamos juntos en silencio, viendo pasar a la multitud en ambas direcciones."

# game/episode020.rpy:2084
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_e0de956a:

#   "We'd fallen in to a companionable reverie when I suddenly felt Raene tense up beside me."
    "Nos habíamos sumido en una agradable ensoñación cuando de repente sentí que Raene se tensaba a mi lado."

# game/episode020.rpy:2087
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_68ae24ae:

#   "Her soft hand suddenly gripped mine, and I could hear her breathing in panic."
    "Su suave mano agarró de pronto la mía y pude oír su respiración de pánico."

# game/episode020.rpy:2089
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_2b151286:

#   "Her hand suddenly gripped mine, and I could hear her breathing in panic."
    "Su mano agarró la mía de repente y pude oír su respiración de pánico."

# game/episode020.rpy:2090
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_e10b424a:

#   c "What's the matter, Raene?"
    c "¿Qué pasa, Raene?"

# game/episode020.rpy:2092
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_a7a9f9a0:

#   ra "It's...{w} I..."
    ra "Es...{w} I..."

# game/episode020.rpy:2093
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_bd6c10f9:

#   ra "We have to go."
    ra "Tenemos que irnos."

# game/episode020.rpy:2094
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_a3a5acfc:

#   "She motioned towards a group of men marching from the direction of the landing pad."
    "Señaló a un grupo de hombres que marchaban en dirección a la pista de aterrizaje."

# game/episode020.rpy:2095
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_c7507496:

#   "They wore identical black clothing, not military, but robes of a sort."
    "Vestían idénticas ropas negras, no militares, sino una especie de túnicas."

# game/episode020.rpy:2096
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_e2ed5079:

#   "The men's expressions ranged from forbidding sternness to outright hostility."
    "Las expresiones de los hombres oscilaban entre la severidad prohibitiva y la hostilidad más absoluta."

# game/episode020.rpy:2097
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_23d0052c:

#   "It wasn't much of surprise that most people gave them a wide berth."
    "No fue una gran sorpresa que la mayoría de la gente les diera la espalda."

# game/episode020.rpy:2099
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_7f1db3f2:

#   "Raene had stood up and was pulling me from the bench as well."
    "Raene se había levantado y tiraba también de mí desde el banco."

# game/episode020.rpy:2100
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_bf0d5cc7:

#   ra "Please, we have to go!"
    ra "¡Por favor, tenemos que irnos!"

# game/episode020.rpy:2101
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_018ca6d3:

#   ra "Those are clerics from the Church of Radiant Dawn."
    ra "Son clérigos de la Iglesia del Amanecer Radiante."

# game/episode020.rpy:2102
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_29f4ed48:

#   c "Your father's men?"
    c "¿Los hombres de tu padre?"

# game/episode020.rpy:2103
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_d8b2dee8:

#   "I stood up as well, realization washing over me."
    "Yo también me levanté y me di cuenta."

# game/episode020.rpy:2104
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_ed475543:

#   ra "Yes."
    ra "Sí."

# game/episode020.rpy:2105
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_b181a0a0:

#   c "Let's go then."
    c "Vamos entonces."

# game/episode020.rpy:2107
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_74e0ef1a:

#   "Just as we attempted to blend into the crowd, two of the men looked at us directly."
    "Justo cuando intentábamos mezclarnos entre la multitud, dos de los hombres nos miraron directamente."

# game/episode020.rpy:2109
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_7a6e934d:

#   "We vanished in the throng and the moment passed, but there was no telling if we were recognized."
    "Desaparecimos entre la multitud y el momento pasó, pero no se sabía si nos habían reconocido."

# game/episode020.rpy:2110
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_93da8297:

#   "Raene and I tried to put as much distance between the clerics and us as possible."
    "Raene y yo intentamos poner la mayor distancia posible entre los clérigos y nosotros."

# game/episode020.rpy:2112
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_2b12032b:

#   "We hurried back to my room where Raene sank onto the bed and buried her head in her hands."
    "Nos apresuramos a volver a mi habitación, donde Raene se hundió en la cama y enterró la cabeza entre las manos."

# game/episode020.rpy:2117
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_e269eec8:

#   "I sat next to her and put an arm around her shoulders."
    "Me senté a su lado y le pasé un brazo por los hombros."

# game/episode020.rpy:2118
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_d89eae46:

#   c "It's unlikely they were here for us."
    c "Es poco probable que estuvieran aquí por nosotros."

# game/episode020.rpy:2119
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_5892dc86:

#   c "Isn't the church on a constant mission to try and recruit new members on any world they can safely land?"
    c "¿No está la Iglesia en una misión constante para intentar reclutar nuevos miembros en cualquier mundo en el que puedan aterrizar con seguridad?"

# game/episode020.rpy:2121
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_df7de432:

#   ra "I know...{w} I know..."
    ra "Lo sé...{w} Lo sé..."

# game/episode020.rpy:2123
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_ac6aac6a:

#   ra "But they saw us, didn't they?"
    ra "Pero nos vieron, ¿no?"

# game/episode020.rpy:2124
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_95b5b449:

#   c "I'm not sure they recognized us."
    c "No estoy seguro de que nos reconocieran."

# game/episode020.rpy:2126
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_4fdcbd32:

#   ra "Those clerics are disciplined and well-trained."
    ra "Esos clérigos son disciplinados y están bien entrenados."

# game/episode020.rpy:2127
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_98f88acc:

#   ra "If my father gave the order to apprehend me, it's almost certain they've memorized my appearance."
    ra "Si mi padre dio la orden de detenerme, es casi seguro que han memorizado mi aspecto."

# game/episode020.rpy:2128
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_750a3088:

#   c "They only saw us as we were about to leave."
    c "Sólo nos vieron cuando estábamos a punto de irnos."

# game/episode020.rpy:2129
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_2ac04bf7:

#   c "It couldn't have been more than just a flash."
    c "No pudo ser más que un destello."

# game/episode020.rpy:2131
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_8ca7a370:

#   ra "But what if they recognized our ship on the landing pad?"
    ra "Pero, ¿y si reconocen nuestra nave en la pista de aterrizaje?"

# game/episode020.rpy:2132
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_8b5674d6:

#   c "If they did, they wouldn't have strolled into the Residence like they did."
    c "Si así fuera, no habrían entrado en la Residencia como lo hicieron."

# game/episode020.rpy:2133
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_68c693db:

#   c "And we passed the landing pad of the Bastard on our way in, it was deserted, no clerics lying in wait."
    c "Y pasamos por la pista de aterrizaje del Bastardo en nuestro camino, estaba desierta, sin clérigos al acecho."

# game/episode020.rpy:2135
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_50163f5a:

#   "I could tell my words did something to calm Raene, but she was still trembling beside me."
    "Me di cuenta de que mis palabras habían calmado a Raene, pero seguía temblando a mi lado."

# game/episode020.rpy:2136
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_cca72f68:

#   c "You're safe here with me."
    c "Estás a salvo aquí conmigo."

# game/episode020.rpy:2137
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_197f7ba6:

#   c "And we'll be leaving as soon as possible."
    c "Y nos iremos lo antes posible."

# game/episode020.rpy:2139
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_6e969be0:

#   ra "Can I stay here until we leave?"
    ra "¿Puedo quedarme aquí hasta que nos vayamos?"

# game/episode020.rpy:2140
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_c4d17d34:

#   ra "I don't want go out and bump into those men."
    ra "No quiero salir y toparme con esos hombres."

# game/episode020.rpy:2141
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_96fecaec:

#   c "Of course you can stay."
    c "Claro que puedes quedarte."

# game/episode020.rpy:2143
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_3d721f44:

#   c "We'll order room service and stay inside until the Bastard is ready for take off."
    c "Pediremos servicio de habitaciones y nos quedaremos dentro hasta que el Bastardo esté listo para despegar."

# game/episode020.rpy:2144
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_e2349592:

#   c "Just think of it as a romantic getaway."
    c "Piensa en ello como una escapada romántica."

# game/episode020.rpy:2146
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_7d3d4998:

#   c "Make yourself at home, order room service if you like and stay inside until the Bastard is ready for take off."
    c "Siéntete como en casa, pide servicio de habitaciones si quieres y quédate dentro hasta que el Bastardo esté listo para despegar."

# game/episode020.rpy:2148
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_0050b436:

#   "Raene looked up and smiled at me."
    "Raene levantó la vista y me sonrió."

# game/episode020.rpy:2149
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_21207c8b:

#   ra "Okay, I'd like that."
    ra "Vale, me gustaría."

# game/episode020.rpy:2150
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_9aa7645f:

#   c "That's settled then."
    c "Eso está arreglado entonces."

# game/episode020.rpy:2151
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_86993e5e:

#   c "I'll notify the others that Radiant Dawn is here and they need to avoid them at all costs."
    c "Notificaré a los demás que Amanecer Radiante está aquí y que deben evitarlos a toda costa."

# game/episode020.rpy:2153
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_741eb44e:

#   "Raene nodded as I began to dispatch messages to the crew."
    "Raene asintió mientras yo empezaba a enviar mensajes a la tripulación."

# game/episode020.rpy:2154
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_7ccaa5e7:

#   c "All done."
    c "Todo hecho."

# game/episode020.rpy:2157
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_f966febf:

#   "I sat back next to her."
    "Me senté a su lado."

# game/episode020.rpy:2158
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_30472a24:

#   c "I'll stay with you here, but I might need to meet up with some of the others at some point."
    c "Me quedaré aquí contigo, pero puede que necesite reunirme con algunos de los otros en algún momento."

# game/episode020.rpy:2159
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_4464e6c6:

#   c "I'll be careful to stay clear of your father's men."
    c "Tendré cuidado de mantenerme alejado de los hombres de tu padre."

# game/episode020.rpy:2164
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_b960fe28:

#   ra "Okay..."
    ra "Bueno..."

# game/episode020.rpy:2165
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_1bb7eccf:

#   ra "I've been so stupid."
    ra "He sido tan estúpida."

# game/episode020.rpy:2166
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_bb00a52c:

#   c "What do you mean?"
    c "¿A qué te refieres?"

# game/episode020.rpy:2171
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_0ae7a656:

#   ra "We knew the church was looking for me."
    ra "Sabíamos que la iglesia me estaba buscando."

# game/episode020.rpy:2172
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_71c7997c:

#   ra "I should have stayed out of sight more."
    ra "Debería haberme mantenido más fuera de la vista."

# game/episode020.rpy:2177
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_7157c5e7:

#   ra "I've been too complacent."
    ra "He sido demasiado complaciente."

# game/episode020.rpy:2178
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_823eb3f9:

#   c "Nonsense, this is just a spot of bad luck."
    c "Tonterías, es sólo un golpe de mala suerte."

# game/episode020.rpy:2179
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_39d6494a:

#   c "Would you have preferred to stay caged inside the Bastard on the off-chance that we'd run into trouble?"
    c "¿Hubieras preferido quedarte enjaulado dentro del Bastardo por si acaso nos encontrábamos con problemas?"

# game/episode020.rpy:2180
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_9cabb5d6:

#   c "That's no way to live."
    c "Esa no es forma de vivir."

# game/episode020.rpy:2185
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_f0d98f72:

#   ra "I guess not. "
    ra "Supongo que no. "

# game/episode020.rpy:2186
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_c79093e3:

#   ra "Truth is, that I'd almost forgotten about it."
    ra "La verdad es que casi lo había olvidado."

# game/episode020.rpy:2187
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_d9e33406:

#   ra "Well, not exactly forgotten, but being with you... being myself..."
    ra "Bueno, no exactamente olvidado, pero estar contigo... ser yo mismo..."

# game/episode020.rpy:2192
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_0d9841ed:

#   ra "All the trouble with my father just started to seem like something from another life."
    ra "Todos los problemas con mi padre empezaron a parecer algo de otra vida."

# game/episode020.rpy:2193
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_bd82c14a:

#   c "It is, actually."
    c "Lo es, en realidad."

# game/episode020.rpy:2194
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_824b3749:

#   c "You've become the person you've always wanted to be and we will not allow the past to mess that all up."
    c "Te has convertido en la persona que siempre quisiste ser y no permitiremos que el pasado lo estropee todo."

# game/episode020.rpy:2195
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_eaf6643a:

#   ra "I just hate that it still has a hold on me."
    ra "Odio que todavía tenga algo contra mí."

# game/episode020.rpy:2196
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_41e6fe99:

#   ra "I've been so happy, but now I fear it could all be yanked away in an instant."
    ra "He sido tan feliz, pero ahora temo que todo se vaya al traste en un instante."

# game/episode020.rpy:2197
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_f5e1059e:

#   c "I won't let that happen, we both are not going to let that happen."
    c "No dejaré que eso suceda, ambos no dejaremos que eso suceda."

# game/episode020.rpy:2200
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_23b6bd9e:

#   "I kissed Raene's tears away and held her close to me."
    "Le quité las lágrimas a Raene con un beso y la estreché contra mí."

# game/episode020.rpy:2201
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_1505c4f3:

#   "I could feel her heart hammering in her chest, her body still in thrall of the panic that had seized her earlier."
    "Sentía su corazón martilleándole en el pecho, su cuerpo aún presa del pánico que se había apoderado de ella antes."

# game/episode020.rpy:2203
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_b0d1beb4:

#   "When her pulse started to slow down, I eased her onto the bed."
    "Cuando su pulso empezó a disminuir, la senté en la cama."

# game/episode020.rpy:2204
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_1bbb07d5:

#   "In the comfort of my arms she fell asleep and I soon followed."
    "En la comodidad de mis brazos se quedó dormida y yo no tardé en seguirla."

# game/episode020.rpy:2207
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_a763a0b1:

#   ra "Thank you, [p_name], you don’t know half how much that means to me."
    ra "Gracias, [p_name], no sabes ni la mitad de lo que significa para mí."

# game/episode020.rpy:2208
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_b9d37965:

#   c "Are you going to be okay on your own for a while?"
    c "¿Vas a estar bien por tu cuenta durante un tiempo?"

# game/episode020.rpy:2209
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_fdbde01a:

#   ra "Yes, I think I’ll be okay."
    ra "Sí, creo que estaré bien."

# game/episode020.rpy:2210
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_fe02bdb8:

#   c "I need to run some errands, but I’ll be back soon."
    c "Tengo que hacer unos recados, pero volveré pronto."

# game/episode020.rpy:2211
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_raene_263d9d30:

#   ra "Okay, see you soon."
    ra "Vale, hasta pronto."

# game/episode020.rpy:2221
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_e10325f2:

#   "Late in the morning, Lilly knocked on my door."
    "A última hora de la mañana, Lilly llamó a mi puerta."

# game/episode020.rpy:2222
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_4bf8f12b:

#   l "Fancy a walk with me?"
    l "¿Te apetece dar un paseo conmigo?"

# game/episode020.rpy:2223
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_4e8c7062:

#   c "Of course."
    c "Por supuesto."

# game/episode020.rpy:2225
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_e9836ff1:

#   "Lilly and I headed out of the Residence and headed towards the forest."
    "Lilly y yo salimos de la Residencia y nos dirigimos hacia el bosque."

# game/episode020.rpy:2227
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_6d996b7f:

#   l "I walked to the forest with Aven yesterday, it’s beautiful there."
    l "Ayer fui al bosque con Aven, es precioso."

# game/episode020.rpy:2229
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_3ad2dea3:

#   c "I know, I went with Jade earlier."
    c "Lo sé, fui con Jade antes."

# game/episode020.rpy:2231
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_93615229:

#   l "Oh, I didn’t know Jade was such an outdoorsy type?"
    l "Oh, no sabía que Jade era un tipo de aire libre."

# game/episode020.rpy:2232
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_81a67d5c:

#   c "I’m not sure she is, but there’s a monument for her mother in the forest."
    c "No estoy seguro de que lo sea, pero hay un monumento a su madre en el bosque."

# game/episode020.rpy:2233
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_e47754ef:

#   l "She mentioned something about that."
    l "Ella mencionó algo sobre eso."

# game/episode020.rpy:2234
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_29fe5c67:

#   l "I didn’t realize it was this close to the Residence."
    l "No sabía que estaba tan cerca de la Residencia."

# game/episode020.rpy:2235
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_13892505:

#   l "Aven and I didn’t see it on our walk though."
    l "Sin embargo, Aven y yo no lo vimos en nuestro paseo."

# game/episode020.rpy:2236
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_52bb3a7f:

#   c "You have to know where to look for it, I think."
    c "Creo que hay que saber dónde buscarlo."

# game/episode020.rpy:2238
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_b0acd8e3:

#   c "Really, it seems a little wild from my balcony."
    c "Realmente, parece un poco salvaje desde mi balcón."

# game/episode020.rpy:2240
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_0b573ec9:

#   l "I’m sure it seemed that way from up in your ivory tower..."
    l "Estoy seguro de que eso parecía desde tu torre de marfil..."

# game/episode020.rpy:2241
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_f722a88e:

#   l "It’s lovely though, you’ll see."
    l "Pero es precioso, ya lo verás."

# game/episode020.rpy:2243
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_d5f3ccd1:

#   "Lilly took my hand and guided me into the forest."
    "Lilly me cogió de la mano y me guió hacia el bosque."

# game/episode020.rpy:2244
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_6b8ea30c:

#   "The sun bathed the trees in a healthy glow and the local wildlife could be heard everywhere."
    "El sol bañaba los árboles con un brillo saludable y la fauna local se oía por todas partes."

# game/episode020.rpy:2245
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_de514dff:

#   c "This place seems so very alive."
    c "Este lugar parece tan vivo."

# game/episode020.rpy:2247
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_304ab562:

#   l "It does, doesn’t it?"
    l "Sí, ¿verdad?"

# game/episode020.rpy:2248
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_c066ba0c:

#   l "I wonder if there are any deserts here on the planet."
    l "Me pregunto si hay desiertos aquí en el planeta."

# game/episode020.rpy:2249
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_9bca6442:

#   c "I’d be amazed, to be honest."
    c "Me sorprendería, la verdad."

# game/episode020.rpy:2250
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_3c2f6281:

#   c "It seems to be all oceans and forests."
    c "Parece que todo son océanos y bosques."

# game/episode020.rpy:2256
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_c1122132:

#   l "[p_name_short], I was wondering something."
    l "[p_name_short], me estaba preguntando algo."

# game/episode020.rpy:2257
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_fe5f3366:

#   c "Okay."
    c "De acuerdo."

# game/episode020.rpy:2258
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_e3649dd7:

#   l "You and Céline were close, right?"
    l "Tú y Céline estabais unidos, ¿verdad?"

# game/episode020.rpy:2259
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_0a6d413c:

#   c "I'd like to think we still are close friends."
    c "Me gustaría pensar que seguimos siendo amigos íntimos."

# game/episode020.rpy:2261
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_cb94709a:

#   l "No, I mean romantically."
    l "No, quiero decir románticamente."

# game/episode020.rpy:2262
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_aed5c73d:

#   l "Back at the Academy, it seemed that you were destined for one another."
    l "En la Academia, parecía que estabais destinados el uno para el otro."

# game/episode020.rpy:2263
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_63f6feb1:

#   l "She couldn't shut up about you either."
    l "Ella tampoco podía dejar de hablar de ti."

# game/episode020.rpy:2264
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_b89f3b41:

#   c "I guess she was interested in me at first, but nothing ever came of it."
    c "Supongo que al principio se interesó por mí, pero nunca llegó a nada."

# game/episode020.rpy:2265
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_9803d365:

#   l "Right..."
    l "Bien..."

# game/episode020.rpy:2266
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_8d601ea3:

#   c "I do get why you might be worried and it's something I've been meaning to talk to you about."
    c "Entiendo por qué puedes estar preocupada y es algo de lo que quería hablarte."

# game/episode020.rpy:2268
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_1681dc26:

#   l "Okay."
    l "De acuerdo."

# game/episode020.rpy:2269
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_c991a3f9:

#   c "What we have is unconventional and very special."
    c "Lo que tenemos es poco convencional y muy especial."

# game/episode020.rpy:2270
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_4077d0ba:

#   c "And it's something I cherish."
    c "Y es algo que aprecio."

# game/episode020.rpy:2272
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_b2e578a8:

#   c "You're the most important person in my life, Lilly."
    c "Eres la persona más importante de mi vida, Lilly."

# game/episode020.rpy:2273
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_89b9f2e1:

#   c "And yes, you're the only one for me."
    c "Y sí, eres el único para mí."

# game/episode020.rpy:2275
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_28dfd366:

#   l "That makes me so very happy to hear!"
    l "Me alegra mucho oírlo."

# game/episode020.rpy:2277
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_31e2bf0c:

#   c "You're one of the most important people in my life, Lilly."
    c "Eres una de las personas más importantes de mi vida, Lilly."

# game/episode020.rpy:2278
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_6d2891a5:

#   c "That said, I cannot commit myself to just one person."
    c "Dicho esto, no puedo comprometerme con una sola persona."

# game/episode020.rpy:2280
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_c57488ca:

#   l "Who else is there?"
    l "¿Quién más hay?"

# game/episode020.rpy:2281
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_cfa6ca55:

#   c "[romances]."
    c "[romances]."

# game/episode020.rpy:2285
translate spanish ep020_paclerara_lilly_b4b73667:

#   l "My mother and sisters..."
    l "Mi madre y mis hermanas..."

# game/episode020.rpy:2287
